0presence%20in%20any%20alliance%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20provide%20the%20Awami%20League%20with%20a%20pretext%20to%20hold%20an%20election%20similar%20to%20that%20of%202014%2C%20in%20which%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Farchive.ipu.org%2Fparline%2Freports%2F2023_E.htm%5C%22%3E153%20contestants%20were%20elected%20unopposed%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Bangladesh%E2%80%99s%20parliament%20constitutes%20300%20members.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHounded%20by%20the%20Awami%20League%20government%20and%20left%20in%20the%20lurch%20by%20its%20long-time%20ally%2C%20Jamaat%20is%20in%20the%20soup.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIt%20can%20make%20a%20backroom%20deal%20with%20the%20Awami%20League%2C%20so%20that%20its%20leaders%20can%20participate%20in%20the%20next%20election%20as%20independent%20candidates.%20But%20given%20their%20recent%20history%2C%20it%20will%20be%20difficult%20%E2%80%93%20if%20not%20impossible%20%E2%80%93%20for%20Jamaat%20to%20trust%20the%20ruling%20party.%20It%20can%20participate%20in%20the%20election%20under%20the%20banner%20of%20the%20Bangladesh%20Development%20Party%2C%20a%20new%20political%20outfit%20which%20many%20believe%20is%20Jamaat%20in%20disguise.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2015%2F06%2FSheikh_Hasina1.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Bangladesh%20Prime%20Minister%20Sheikh%20Hasina.%20Credit%3A%20Wikimedia%20Commons%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221280%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2015%2F06%2FSheikh_Hasina1.jpg%201280w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2015%2F06%2FSheikh_Hasina1-300x159.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2015%2F06%2FSheikh_Hasina1-1024x543.jpg%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-3188%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22679%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3ESheikh%20Hasina%2C%20Bangladesh%20Prime%20Minister%20and%20leader%20of%20the%20Awami%20League.%20Credit%3A%20Wikimedia%20Commons%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3EBut%20participating%20in%20any%20kind%20of%20polls%20that%20are%20not%20inclusive%20or%20boycotted%20by%20most%20of%20the%20major%20political%20parties%20can%20even%20lead%20to%20the%20split%20of%20Jamaat.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ETo%20make%20matters%20worse%2C%20Jamaat%20has%20become%20a%20relic%20of%20the%20Cold%20War.%20The%20party%2C%20a%20group%20similar%20to%20Muslim%20brotherhood%2C%20has%20been%20crucial%20for%20the%20US%20in%20the%20early%20and%20late%201970s%20as%20its%20role%20was%20pivotal%20in%20fighting%20the%20Left%20in%20the%20Muslim%20majority%20Bangladesh%20and%20Pakistan.%20During%20the%20so-called%20%E2%80%98war%20on%20terror%E2%80%99%2C%20Jamaat%20kept%20a%20centrist%20position.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ENow%20that%20the%20US%E2%80%99s%20interest%20is%20more%20centred%20around%20containing%20China%20in%20the%20Indo-Pacific%20region%2C%20the%20party%20will%20find%20it%20difficult%20to%20make%20itself%20look%20useful.%20Also%20troubling%20for%20Jamaat%20is%20its%20leadership%E2%80%99s%20apparent%20inability%20to%20find%20its%20role%20in%20this%20changed%20world.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EProblematic%2C%20too%2C%20is%20its%20Leninist%20party%20structure%2C%20which%20is%20good%20for%20a%20revolutionary%20party.%20But%20Jamaat%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20have%20any%20big%20mass%20organisation%20from%20which%20it%20can%20draw%20new%20members.%20This%20lack%20of%20inclusiveness%20has%20made%20the%20party%20appear%20to%20look%20like%20a%20self-limiting%2C%20annoying%20condition%20that%20neither%20goes%20away%20nor%20puts%20its%20bearer%20in%20harm%E2%80%99s%20way.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EJamaat%20in%20Bangladesh%E2%80%99s%20politics%20is%20increasingly%20becoming%20irrelevant.%20A%20deal%20brokered%20by%20India%2C%20which%20will%20oversee%20Jamaat%20leaders%E2%80%99%20participation%20in%20the%20election%20under%20the%20Awami%20League%20can%20give%20the%20regime%20in%20Dhaka%20some%20breathing%20space.%20It%20will%20also%20give%20Jamaat%20a%20straw%20to%20clutch%20at.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHaving%20said%20that%2C%20India%20should%20keep%20in%20mind%20that%20a%20just%2C%20free%20and%20democratic%20Bangladesh%20is%20important%20for%20the%20stability%20of%20the%20region.%20India%20needs%20to%20sit%20with%20all%20major%20political%20actors%20in%20Bangladesh%2C%20including%20the%20US%2C%20in%20order%20to%20make%20sure%20that%20India%E2%80%99s%20security%20concerns%20are%20respected%20by%20the%20party%20that%20will%20come%20to%20power%20through%20a%20free%20and%20fair%20election%20this%20January.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIndia%20and%20Bangladesh%E2%80%99s%20future%20is%20historically%20and%20geographically%20entwined%2C%20and%20it%20should%20be%20a%20democratic%20one.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EAhmede%20Hussain%20is%20a%20Bangladeshi%20writer%20and%20journalist.%20He%E2%80%99s%20the%20editor%20of%20the%20anthology%20%3C%2Fem%3EThe%20New%20Anthem%3A%20the%20Subcontinent%20in%20its%20own%20Words%3Cem%3E%20(Tranquebar%3B%20Delhi).%20He%20has%20just%20finished%20writing%20his%20first%20novel.%20His%20X%20handle%20is%20%40ahmedehussain%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1695211253000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F15160712%2FBangladesh-protests.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsouth-asia%2Fjamaat-e-islamis-role-in-bangladesh-elections-and-what-it-means-for-india%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22For%20India%2C%20Jamaat%20is%20a%20red%20flag.%20So%2C%20for%20the%20world%E2%80%99s%20largest%20democracy%2C%20any%20electoral%20change%20in%20Bangladesh%20that%20might%20topple%20the%20Awami%20League%20from%20power%20can%20be%20considered%20a%20cause%20of%20worry.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsouth-asia%2Fjamaat-e-islamis-role-in-bangladesh-elections-and-what-it-means-for-