22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fculture%2Famid-strained-diplomatic-ties-bookmyshow-cancels-canadian-punjabi-singer-shubhs-india-tour%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20decision%20to%20cancel%20Shubhneet%20Singh's%20India%20tour%20was%20preceded%20by%20social%20media%20posts%20calling%20for%20the%20boycott%20of%20the%20booking%20app.%20%23UninstallBookMyShow%20was%20trending%20on%20X%20(formerly%2C%20Twitter).%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fculture%2Famid-strained-diplomatic-ties-bookmyshow-cancels-canadian-punjabi-singer-shubhs-india-tour%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22US%20Says%20Canada's%20Allegations%20%26quot%3BSerious%26quot%3B%2C%20Seeks%20India's%20Cooperation%3A%20Report%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3ETerming%20Canadian%20Prime%20Minister%20Justin%20Trudeau's%20allegations%20about%20India's%20involvement%20in%20the%20killing%20of%20a%20Sikh%20separatist%20leader%20as%20%26quot%3Bvery%20serious%26quot%3B%2C%20a%20top%20US%20official%20has%20said%20that%20Washington%20supports%20Ottawa's%20efforts%20to%20investigate%20the%20matter%20and%20encourages%20New%20Delhi%20to%20cooperate.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI'm%20going%20to%20protect%20diplomatic%20conversations%20and%20I'll%20leave%20it%20at%20that.%20Certainly%20the%20President%20is%20mindful%20of%20these%20serious%20allegations%2C%20and%20they%20are%20very%20serious.%20And%20we%20support%20Canada's%20efforts%20to%20investigate%20this%2C%26quot%3B%20US%20National%20Security%20Council%20(NSC)%20Coordinator%20for%20Strategic%20Communications%20John%20Kirby%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20believe%20a%20fully%20transparent%20comprehensive%20investigation%20is%20the%20right%20approach%20so%20that%20we%20can%20all%20know%20exactly%20what%20happened%20and%20of%20course%2C%20we%20encourage%20India%20to%20cooperate%20with%20that%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Kirby%20said%20in%20an%20interview%20to%20CNN.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMr%20Kirby%20was%20responding%20to%20a%20question%20on%20Mr%20Trudeau's%20allegations%20about%20the%20involvement%20of%20%26quot%3Bagents%20of%20the%20Indian%20government%26quot%3B%20in%20the%20killing%20of%20Hardeep%20Singh%20Nijjar%2C%2045%2C%20the%20chief%20of%20the%20banned%20Khalistan%20Tiger%20Force%20(KTF).%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ENijjar%20was%20one%20of%20India's%20most-wanted%20terrorists%20who%20carried%20a%20cash%20reward%20of%20Rs%2010%20lakh%20on%20his%20head%20and%20was%20shot%20dead%20by%20two%20unidentified%20gunmen%20outside%20a%20gurdwara%20in%20Surrey%20in%20the%20western%20Canadian%20province%20of%20British%20Columbia%20on%20June%2018.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMr%20Kirby%20was%20asked%20about%20Mr%20Trudeau%20raising%20the%20matter%20with%20President%20Joe%20Biden%20privately%20before%20going%20public%20and%20what%20information%20the%20Canadian%20leader%20shared%20with%20the%20US%20President%20about%20the%20matter.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI'm%20going%20to%20be%20careful%20about%20what%20I%20say%20here%20to%20preserve%20the%20sanctity%20of%20this%20investigation%20and%20leave%20it%20for%20Canada%20to%20talk%20about%20the%20underpinning%20information%2C%20what%20more%20they're%20trying%20to%20learn.%20We%20want%20to%20respect%20that%20process%20and%20it's%20their%20investigation%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWhen%20further%20asked%20about%20what%20repercussions%20there%20will%20be%20due%20to%20the%20allegations%2C%20Mr%20Kirby%20said%2C%20%26quot%3Blet's%20not%20get%20ahead%20of%20where%20we%20are.%20There's%20an%20active%20investigation.%20We%20think%20it%20needs%20to%20be%20fully%20transparent%2C%20comprehensive.%20We%20know%20that%20Canadians%20will%20work%20to%20that%20end%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAgain%2C%20we%20urge%20India%20to%20cooperate%20with%20that%20investigation%20so%20that%20the%20facts%20can%20take%20investigators%20where%20they%20go%20and%20then%20once%20we%20have%20all%20that%20facts%2C%20and%20we%20have%20conclusions%20that%20we%20can%20draw%20from%20that%2C%20then%20you%20can%20start%20to%20look%20at%20recommendations%20or%20behaviours%20you%20might%20want%20to%20pursue.%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20an%20interview%20to%20CBS%20News%2C%20Kirby%20said%20that%20%26quot%3Bthese%20allegations%20are%20serious%20and%20we%20know%20that%20the%20Canadians%20are%20investigating%20it.%20We%20certainly%20don't%20want%20to%20get%20ahead%20of%20that%20investigation%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20urge%20India%20to%20cooperate%20in%20that%20investigation%20as%20well.%20This%20is%20the%20kind%20of%20an%20attack%20here%20that%20obviously%20we%20all%20want%20to%20know%20is%20handled%20in%20a%20transparent%2C%20thorough%20way.%20And%20that%20the%20Canadian%20people%20can%20get%20answers%20to%20this.%20So%20we're%20going%20stay%20in%20touch%20with%20our%20partners%2C%20both%20countries%2C%20and%20again%20we%20want%20to%20see%20the%20investigation%20be%20able%20to%20proceed%20unhindered%20and%20let%20the%20facts%20take%20it%20where%20it%20may%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Kirby%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1695210600000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2022-05%2Filgmelik_canadas-justin-trudeau_625x300_09_May_22.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fus-says-canadas-allegations-serious-seeks-indias-cooperation-report-4407172%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Terming%20Canadian%20Prime%20Minister%20Justin%20Trudeau's%20allegations%20about%20India's%20involvement%20in%20the%20killing%20of%20a%20Sikh%20separatist%20leader%20as%20%26quot%3Bvery%20serious%26quot%3B%2C%20a%20top%20US%20official%20has%20said%20that%20Washington%20supports%20Ottawa's%20efforts%20to%20investigate%20the%20matter%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fus-says-canadas-allegations-serious-seeks-indias-cooperation-report-4407172%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22India%20Plans%20%242%20Billion%20In%20Incentives%20For%20New%20Manufacturing%20Sectors%3A%20Report%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EIndia%20is%20planning%20to%20offer%20incentives%20of%20up%20to%20Rs%2018%2C000%20Crore%20(%242.2%20billion)%20to%20spur%20local%20manufacturing%20in%20six%20new%20sectors%20including%20chemicals%2C%20shipping%20containers%20and%20inputs%20for%20vaccines%2C%20two%20government%20officials%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20proposal%20is%20part%20of%20the%20country's%201.97-trillion-rupee%20production-linked%20incentive%20scheme%20(PLI)%2C%20launched%20in%202020%20which%20currently%20targets%2014%20sectors%20ranging%20from%20electronic%20products%20to%20drones%2C%20but%20has%20been%20successful%20only%20in%20a%20handful%20of%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EA%20fraction%20of%20the%20PLI%20incentives%20has%20been%20claimed%20so%20far%2C%20prompting%20the%20government%20to%20allocate%20unused%20funds%20to%20new%20sectors.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ELimited%20payouts%20under%20the%20scheme%20could%20lead%20to%20%26quot%3Blarge%26quot%3B%20savings%20which%20may%20be%20redirected%20to%20new%20sectors%2C%20the%20two%20government%20officials%20with%20knowledge%20of%20the%20plan%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThey%20did%20not%20wish%20to%20be%20named%20as%20details%20of%20the%20plan%20have%20not%20been%20made%20public.%20India's%20federal%20trade%20ministry%20that%20oversees%20the%20scheme's%20implementation%20did%20not%20immediately%20respond%20to%20an%20emailed%20request%20for%20comment.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20six%20new%20sectors%20that%20could%20join%20the%20PLI%20scheme%20also%20include%20toys%2C%20bicycles%2C%20leather%20and%20footwear%2C%20the%20officials%20said.%20These%20sectors%20will%20share%20the%20Rs%2018%2C000%20Crore%20(180-billion-rupee)%20allocation%20that%20is%20being%20carved%20out%20from%20the%20scheme's%20original%20outlay%2C%20they%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIndia%20sees%20the%20PLI%20scheme%20as%20crucial%20to%20boosting%20the%20broader%20Indian%20economy%20which%20has%20been%20starved%20of%20private%20investment%20for%20nearly%20a%20decade%20and%20is%20struggling%20to%20create%20adequate%20jobs%2C%20particularly%20in%20manufacturing.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ETotal%20incentives%20worth%20nearly%2029%20billion%20rupees%20were%20paid%20out%20in%20the%20fiscal%20year%20that%20ended%20in%20March.%20Little%20has%20been%20paid%20to%20businesses%20in%20sectors%20including%20speciality%20steel%20products%2C%20solar%20modules%2C%20and%20car%20components%2C%20according%20to%20a%20government%20report%20seen%20by%20Reuters.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20fiscal%20year%20that%20started%20in%20April%2C%20the%20disbursements%20could%20rise%20to%20nearly%2011%2C000%20Crore%20rupees%20and%20to%2040%2C000%20Crore%20rupees%20by%20fiscal%20year%202024%2F25%2C%20one%20of%20the%20two%20officials%20said%2C%20citing%20an%20internal%20analysis%20by%20the%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20disbursements%20should%20be%20better%20than%20this%20estimate%20after%20some%20tweaks%20to%20the%20scheme%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20official%20said%2C%20adding%20such%20tweaks%20would%20help%20speed%20up%20payouts%20and%20some%20sectors%20may%20get%20an%20additional%20year%20or%20two%20under%20the%20scheme.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1695210540000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2022-11%2Ftragken_metal-factory-generic_625x300_09_November_22.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Findia-plans-2-billion-in-incentives-for-new-manufacturing-sectors-report-4407347%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22India%20is%20planning%20to%20offer%20incentives%20of%20up%20to%20Rs%2018%2C000%20Crore%20(%242.2%20billion)%20to%20spur%20local%20manufacturing%20in%20six%20new%20sectors%20including%20chemicals%2C%20shipping%20containers%20and%20inputs%20for%20vaccines%2C%20two%20government%20officials%20said.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Findia-plans-2-billion-in-incentives-for-new-manufacturing-sectors-report-4407347%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Findia-plans-2-billion-in-incentives-for-new-manufacturing-sectors-report-4407347%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Findia-plans-2-billion-in-incentives-for-new-manufacturing-sectors-report-4407347%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22What%20Actors%20Bhumi%20Pednekar%2C%20Shehnaaz%20Gill%20Said%20On%20Women's%20Quota%20Bill%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EActors%20Bhumi%20Pednekar%20and%20Shehnaaz%20Gill%20visited%20the%20new%20Parliament%20building%20today%20ahead%20of%20the%20release%20of%20their%20upcoming%20movie%20'%3Cem%3EThank%20You%20For%20Coming%3C%2Fem%3E.'%20They%20met%20with%20Union%20Minister%20Anurag%20Thakur%20along%20with%20their%20other%20co-stars%20Shibani%20Bedi%20and%20Dolly%20Singh.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20to%20NDTV%20about%20the%20Nari%20Shakti%20Vandan%20Adhiniyam%2C%20or%20the%20women's%20reservation%20bill%2C%20Bhumi%20Pednekar%20said%3A%20%26quot%3BI%20feel%20very%20proud%20to%20be%20here%20and%20be%20a%20part%20of%20such%20a%20historic%20moment.%20It%20is%20a%20beautiful%20building%20(the%20new%20Parliament).%20Being%20a%20modern%2C%20Indian%20woman%2C%20this%20(women's%20reservation%20bill)%20is%20a%20very%20important%20thing%20for%20us.%20Through%20our%20films%20and%20our%20work%2C%20we%20have%20tried%20to%20maintain%20equality%20for%20our%20gender.%20The%20messaging%20of%20the%20bill%20will%20go%20far%20and%20wide%20-%20change%20is%20here%20and%20our%20tomorrow%20will%20be%20even%20better.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20bill%20will%20bring%20a%20change%20that%20will%20help%20women%20get%20better%20representation.%20If%20there%20are%20no%20women%20in%20places%20of%20power%2C%20the%20policies%20and%20laws%20won't%20be%20proper.%20The%20representation%20will%20happen%20now%2C%20there%20is%20hope%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMs%20Pednekar's%20co-actor%20Shehnaaz%20Gill%20said%20men%20and%20women%20should%20be%20treated%20the%20same.%20%26quot%3BIt%20is%20a%20big%20thing%20for%20me%20...%20Something%20big%20is%20happening%20for%20the%20women%20of%20our%20country%20and%20I%20am%20here.%20I%20am%20here%20on%20a%20historic%20day.%20I%20had%20the%20opportunity%20to%20see%20the%20Parliament%20from%20inside.%20Not%20everyone%20gets%20such%20an%20opportunity.%20I%20even%20heard%20the%20debate%20(on%20the%20women's%20reservation%20bill).%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20is%20a%20good%20thing%20-%20the%20proposal%20to%20have%2033%25%20reservation%20in%20Lok%20Sabha%20and%20state%20assemblies%20for%20women.%20I%20feel%20men%20and%20women%20should%20be%20treated%20the%20same.%20India%20is%20growing%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20felt%20nice%20to%20see%20the%20House%20proceedings%20live%20after%20seeing%20them%20on%20TV%20for%20so%20many%20years.%20We%20went%20around%20the%20complex%20and%20everything%20was%20explained%20to%20us.%20I%20got%20to%20see%20the%20art%20on%20display.%20It%20was%20fantastic%2C%26quot%3B%20Ms%20Gill%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20new%20Parliament%20reverberated%20with%20fiery%20speeches%20from%20women%20MPs%20today%20during%20a%20heated%20debate%20on%20the%20women's%20reservation%20bill.%20Former%20Congress%20chief%20Sonia%20Gandhi%2C%20DMK%20MP%20Kanimozhi%2C%20and%20the%20NCP's%20Supriya%20Sule%20ripped%20into%20the%20government%20for%20failing%20to%20respect%20women%2C%20while%20Union%20Minister%20Smriti%20Irani%20responded%20by%20declaring%20the%20government%20has%20%26quot%3Bmade%20women%20count%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1695210540000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-09%2F4uv7ahq_bhumi-pednekar-parliament-ndtv_625x300_20_September_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fwhat-actors-bhumi-pednekar-shehnaaz-gill-said-on-womens-quota-bill-4407350%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Actors%20Bhumi%20Pednekar%20and%20Shehnaaz%20Gill%20visited%20the%20new%20Parliament%20building%20today%20ahead%20of%20the%20release%20of%20their%20upcoming%20movie%20'Thank%20You%20For%20Coming'.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fwhat-actors-bhumi-pednekar-shehnaaz-gill-said-on-womens-quota-bill-4407350%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fwhat-actors-bhumi-pednekar-shehnaaz-gill-said-on-womens-quota-bill-4407350%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fwhat-actors-bhumi-pednekar-shehnaaz-gill-said-on-womens-quota-bill-4407350%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22'There%20is%20no%20comparison%20between%20Ashwin%20and...'%3A%20Kaif%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1695210386000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-103811916%2Cimgsize-32926.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fsports%2Fcricket%2Faustralia-in-india%2Fthere-is-no-comparison-between-ashwin-and-mohammad-kaif%2Farticleshow%2F103811870.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Ravichandran%20Ashwin's%20return%20to%20the%20ODI%20side%20for%20the%20Australia%20series%20has%20sparked%20debate%20among%20former%20players.%20Ashwin%20was%20included%20after%20Axar%20Patel%20suffered%20a%20quadriceps%20tear%20during%20the%20Asia%20Cup%20and%20missed%20the%20final%20against%20Sri%20Lanka.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20SPORTS%20DESK%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Opinion%3A%20Women's%20Reservation%20Bill%20-%20An%20Epic%20Moment%2C%20Cue%20Uplifting%20Music%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20need%20for%20affirmative%20action%20for%20women%20in%20legislative%20bodies%20has%20been%20articulated%20by%20scholars%20for%20years.%20Political%20scientists%20like%20Anne%20Phillips%20and%20Drude%20Dahlerup%20have%20argued%20that%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Facademic.oup.com%2Fbook%2F7080%5C%22%3E%26quot%3Bpolitics%20of%20presence%26quot%3B%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20crucial%20for%20the%20effective%20functioning%20of%20a%20democratic%20system.%20Without%20women%2C%20who%20constitute%20around%2050%25%20of%20the%20population%2C%20having%20a%20fair%20share%20of%20seats%2C%20legislatures%20lack%20the%20perspectives%20that%20are%20essential%20for%20inclusive%20lawmaking.%20With%20only%2015%25%20of%20women%20legislators%20in%20India's%20House%20of%20the%20People%2C%20their%20underrepresentation%20not%20only%20reveals%20a%20gender%20disparity%20but%20also%20constitutes%20a%20democratic%20deficit.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20move%20by%20the%20Union%20Government%20to%20table%20The%20Constitution%20(One%20Hundred%20and%20Twenty-eighth%20Amendment)%20Bill%2C%202023%2C%20is%20laudable%20on%20multiple%20fronts.%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi's%20announcement%20on%20Ganesh%20Chaturthi%20and%20the%20fact%20that%20this%20was%20the%20first%20bill%20tabled%20in%20the%20new%20Parliament%20building%20makes%20the%20occasion%20memorable.%20This%20is%20part%20of%20the%20democratic%20reforms%20that%20were%20initiated%20by%20Atal%20Bihari%20Vajpayee.%20However%2C%20due%20to%20the%20absence%20of%20political%20support%20across%20the%20party%20lines%2C%20it%20never%20went%20through.%20Now%2C%20the%20government%20under%20PM%20Modi%20has%20taken%20upon%20itself%20to%20ensure%20that%20women's%20presence%20in%20legislative%20bodies%20rise%20to%20at%20least%2033%25%2C%20increasing%20the%20count%20of%20women%20in%20the%20House%20of%20the%20People%20from%20the%20current%2082%20to%20at%20least%20181.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20underrepresentation%20of%20women%20in%20state%20legislative%20assemblies%20is%20even%20more%20glaring.%20Based%20on%20recent%20data%2C%20it's%20abundantly%20clear%20that%20the%20percentage%20of%20women%20legislators%20at%20the%20state%20level%20is%20alarmingly%20low.%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsansad.in%2FgetFile%2Floksabhaquestions%2Fannex%2F1710%2FAU501.pdf%3Fsource%3Dpqals%5C%22%3E%20In%20an%20answer%20to%3C%2Fa%3E%20parliament%20by%20the%20then%20Law%20Minister%20Kiren%20Rijiju%20in%20December%202022%2C%20the%20percentages%20of%20women%20elected%20to%20state%20legislative%20assemblies%20were%20revealed%2C%20and%20the%20numbers%20are%20staggering.%20This%20data%20is%20slightly%20dated%20as%20the%20cut-off%20date%20is%209%20December%202022.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EConsider%20this%3A%20The%20states%20of%20Assam%2C%20Arunachal%20Pradesh%2C%20and%20Karnataka%2C%20for%20example%2C%20have%20fewer%20than%205%25%20of%20their%20legislative%20seats%20occupied%20by%20women.%20Assam%20has%204.76%25%2C%20Arunachal%20Pradesh%205.00%25%2C%20and%20Karnataka%2C%20a%20mere%203.14%25.%20Most%20shocking%20perhaps%20are%20Mizoram%20and%20Nagaland%2C%20where%20not%20a%20single%20woman%20has%20been%20elected%20to%20the%20legislative%20assembly%20as%20of%202018.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20not%20just%20about%20specific%20states.%20It's%20a%20nationwide%20concern.%20Even%20states%20like%20Bihar%20and%20Haryana%2C%20which%20have%20crossed%20the%2010%25%20threshold%2C%20only%20have%2010.70%25%20and%2010.00%25%20female%20representation.%20Across%20the%20board%2C%20there%20gaping%20disparity.%20The%20bill%20will%20address%20this%20very%20issue.%20Women's%20issues%20can't%20be%20fully%20addressed%20if%20only%20about%2015%25%20of%20state%20legislators%20are%20women.%20Legislation%20reflects%20the%20values%20of%20those%20who%20make%20it%2C%20so%20this%20lack%20of%20representation%20is%20problematic.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIt's%20not%20just%20about%20gender%20equality%3B%20having%20more%20women%20in%20politics%20improves%20the%20system%20and%20society.%20Their%20absence%20alienates%20many%20women%2C%20undermining%20the%20system's%20legitimacy.%20Research%20indicates%20that%20when%20more%20women%20hold%20political%20roles%2C%20it%20boosts%20political%20participation%20among%20women%2C%20debunking%20the%20notion%20that%20politics%20is%20an%20all-male%20sphere.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMoreover%2C%20the%20presence%20of%20women%20in%20politics%20serves%20as%20a%20potent%20role%20model%20effect.%20Women%20in%20high%20office%20dispel%20the%20myth%20of%20politics%20being%20unattainable%20for%20other%20women%2C%20encouraging%20them%20to%20consider%20political%20careers.%20Female%20politicians%20are%20more%20likely%20to%20advocate%20for%20policies%20and%20legislation%20that%20directly%20affect%20women's%20lives%2C%20thereby%20promoting%20a%20political%20agenda%20that%20is%20more%20inclusive%20and%20representative%20of%20the%20population's%20needs.%20The%20direct%20correlation%20between%20women%20in%20power%20and%20women-centric%20policies%20can%20heighten%20the%20sense%20of%20political%20efficacy%20among%20female%20citizens%2C%20inspiring%20more%20active%20participation.%20They're%20more%20likely%20to%20advocate%20for%20policies%20affecting%20women%2C%20making%20politics%20more%20inclusive%20and%20representative.%20Finally%2C%20female%20politicians%20often%20bring%20different%20styles%20and%20priorities%2C%20making%20political%20settings%20more%20welcoming%20for%20women%20and%20fostering%20a%20more%20effective%20system.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWestern%20liberal%20democracies%20frequently%20lecture%20India%20on%20its%20commitment%20to%20democratic%20values.%20While%20V-Dem%20controversially%20labels%20India%20as%20an%20%26quot%3Belectoral%20autocracy%26quot%3B%2C%20it's%20worth%20noting%20that%20India%20stands%20distinctively%20ahead%20in%20substantive%20areas%20which%20these%20countries%20are%20now%20terming%20as%20democratic.%20India%20is%20the%20only%20major%20democracy%20with%20affirmative%20action%20for%20women%20in%20local%20bodies.%20If%20the%20proposed%20bill%20becomes%20law%20and%20is%20enacted%2C%20not%20only%20will%20the%20number%20of%20women%20in%20state%20legislatures%20and%20the%20House%20of%20the%20People%20see%20a%20significant%20increase%2C%20but%20India%20will%20also%20set%20a%20unique%20precedent%20as%20the%20only%20major%20democracy%20in%20the%20world%20to%20implement%20such%20affirmative%20action.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ENotably%2C%20the%20bill%20also%20has%20a%20temporal%20framework-after%20an%20initial%20period%20of%2015%20years%2C%20its%20term%20can%20be%20extended%2C%20providing%20a%20measured%20and%20evaluative%20approach%20to%20a%20long-standing%20issue.%20While%20some%20may%20argue%20that%20the%20bill%20won't%20take%20effect%20at%20least%20before%202029%20elections%20due%20to%20the%20delimitation%20and%20census%20processes%2C%20the%20legislation%20sets%20the%20stage%20for%20a%20future%20where%20women%20will%20play%20a%20more%20substantial%20role%20in%20the%20political%20sphere%2C%20not%20as%20a%20token%20but%20as%20a%20rightful%20part%20of%20the%20democratic%20process.%20In%20a%20world%20where%20the%20contributions%20of%20Indian%20women%20are%20being%20increasingly%20recognized%2C%20from%20sports%20to%20startups%2C%20this%20legislative%20move%20is%20not%20just%20timely%20but%20integral%20to%20India's%20democratic%20ethos.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20words%20of%20Professor%20Albus%20Dumbledore%20from%20J.K.%20Rowling's%20%26quot%3BHarry%20Potter%26quot%3B%20series%2C%20%26quot%3BWe%20must%20all%20face%20the%20choice%20between%20what%20is%20right%20and%20what%20is%20easy.%26quot%3B%20For%20far%20too%20long%2C%20Indian%20politics%20has%20taken%20the%20easy%20route%2C%20sidelining%20the%20voices%20and%20perspectives%20of%2050%25%20of%20its%20population.%20Scholars%20like%20Anne%20Phillips%20have%20pointed%20out%20the%20gaping%20hole%20in%20any%20democratic%20setup%20due%20to%20the%20underrepresentation%20of%20women%20for%20years%2C%20and%20now%20it%20seems%20the%20government%20is%20finally%20willing%20to%20mend%20it.%20The%20introduction%20of%20The%20Constitution%20(One%20Hundred%20and%20Twenty-eighth%20Amendment)%20Bill%2C%202023%2C%20is%20akin%20to%20the%20epic%20moment%20in%20cinema%20when%20the%20underdog%20steps%20up%2C%20cue%20uplifting%20music%2C%20and%20everyone%20wonders%20why%20it%20took%20so%20long%20to%20recognize%20the%20potential.%20Sure%2C%20the%20bill%20isn't%20a%20magical%20fix%2C%20but%20it's%20a%20step%20forward.%20A%20crucial%20one.%20And%20for%20that%2C%20even%20Dumbledore%20would%20give%20it%20an%20approving%20nod-twinkling%20eyes%20and%20all.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EBibek%20Debroy%20is%20the%20Chairman%2C%20Economic%20Advisory%20Council%20to%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20(EAC-PM)%20%26amp%3B%20Aditya%20Sinha%20is%20Additional%20Private%20Secretary%20(Policy%20%26amp%3B%20Research)%2C%20EAC-PM.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDisclaimer%3A%20These%20are%20the%20personal%20opinions%20of%20the%20author.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1695210060000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-09%2Fovml5cm8_new-parliament_625x300_20_September_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fwomens-reservation-bill-an-epic-moment-cue-uplifting-music-4407293%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20need%20for%20affirmative%20action%20for%20women%20in%20legislative%20bodies%20has%20been%20articulated%20by%20scholars%20for%20years.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fwomens-reservation-bill-an-epic-moment-cue-uplifting-music-4407293%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.amp