E.%20This%20is%20big%20because%20the%20Canadians%20have%20accused%20the%20Indian%20government%20%E2%80%93%20not%20any%20private%20vigilante%20group%20or%20organisation%20%E2%80%93%20of%20murder%20in%20a%20foreign%20land.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ETrudeau%20and%20Canadian%20state%20services%20seem%20to%20have%20taken%20this%20as%20seriously%20as%20the%20UK%20did%20when%20the%20Russian%20%C3%A9migr%C3%A9%20Alexander%20Litvinenko%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.npr.org%2F2021%2F09%2F21%2F1039224996%2Frussia-alexander-litvinenko-european-court-human-rights-putin%5C%22%3Ewas%20killed%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20allegedly%20on%20orders%20of%20the%20Kremlin.%20It%20is%20extraordinarily%20rare%20for%20a%20Western%20democracy%20to%20expel%20a%20diplomat%20from%20another%20democracy%20on%20these%20grounds.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%20%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EThis%20is%201st%20time%20a%20foreign%20govt%2C%20barring%20Pakistan%2C%20has%20accused%20Delhi%20of%20an%20act%20of%20violence%20on%20their%20soil.%20At%20the%20same%20time%2C%20allegations%20that%20Indian%20forces%2Fagents%20acted%20abroad%20in%20contravention%20of%20intl%20law%20were%20made%20recently%20in%20two%20high%20profile%20cases.%201%2F2%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FsY5VfbPrX0%5C%22%3Ehttps%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FsY5VfbPrX0%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%94%20Siddharth%20(%40svaradarajan)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fsvaradarajan%2Fstatus%2F1704037410269458905%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3ESeptember%2019%2C%202023%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20theory%2C%20this%20ought%20to%20be%20a%20major%20embarrassment%20for%20Modi.%20Western%20media%20headlines%20will%20not%20be%20flattering%20for%20a%20few%20days%20but%20he%20is%20bound%20to%20weather%20this.%20In%20fact%2C%20the%20altercation%20with%20Canada%20is%20likely%20to%20serve%20him%20politically%20well%20at%20home.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20because%20Nijjar%2C%20the%20Sikh%20leader%20who%20was%20killed%2C%20is%20accused%20of%20being%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fglobalnews.ca%2Fnews%2F9969537%2Fwho-is-hardeep-singh-nijjar%2F%5C%22%3Eterrorist%3C%2Fa%3E%20by%20India.%20New%20Delhi%20claims%20that%20he%20was%20the%20mastermind%20of%20the%20separatist%20militant%20group%2C%20Khalistan%20Tiger%20Force.%20Nijjar%20was%20an%20accused%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fworld%2Fhardeep-singh-nijjar-killing-khalistan-speculation%5C%22%3Eseveral%20terrorist%20cases%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20named%20in%20an%20Interpol%20notice%20as%20a%20%E2%80%9Ckey%20conspirator%E2%80%9D%20in%20a%202007%20bombing%20of%20a%20cinema%20in%20Punjab.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EModi%20gains%20from%20this%20because%20his%20base%20has%20a%20tendency%20to%20celebrate%20aggressive%20initiatives%20against%20adversaries.%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20fans%20were%20jubilant%20when%20the%20Indian%20Air%20Force%20conducted%20airstrikes%20in%20the%20Pakistani%20territory%20after%20the%20terrorist%20attack%20in%20Pulwama%20in%202019.%20The%20alleged%20act%20of%20organising%20a%20terrorist%E2%80%99s%20assassination%20in%20a%20foreign%20land%20would%20seem%20quite%20redolent%20of%20Mossad%E2%80%99s%20ways%2C%20which%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20fans%20adore.%20Expect%20Modi%20to%20be%20hailed%2C%20those%20involved%20to%20become%20heroes%2C%20and%20perhaps%20a%20movie%20script%20may%20follow.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20Indian%20media%20will%20explain%20this%20away%20as%20Trudeau%20pandering%20to%20the%20Sikh%20vote%20in%20Canada.%20Trudeau%E2%80%99s%20move%20may%20not%20be%20bereft%20of%20political%20calculation%3B%20he%20may%20also%20be%20caught%20between%20the%20findings%20of%20the%20Canadian%20law%20enforcement%20%E2%80%93%20that%20he%20would%20have%20to%20act%20on%20%E2%80%93%20and%20the%20official%20need%20to%20maintain%20ties%20with%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EFrom%20Canada%E2%80%99s%20point%20of%20view%2C%20the%20Modi%20government%20did%20transgress%20established%20norms%20between%20political%20elites.%20There%20are%20processes%20about%20dealing%20with%20terrorists%20residing%20in%20other%20countries.%20Trudeau%E2%80%99s%20view%20would%20be%20that%20you%20just%20don%E2%80%99t%20take%20out%20people%20if%20those%20processes%20do%20not%20work%20for%20you.%20There%20are%20rules%20to%20follow%20and%20colleagues%20in%20the%20governing%20class%20do%20not%20create%20domestic%20political%20situations%20and%20problems%20for%20each%20other.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThat%20said%20this%20controversy%20should%20make%20no%20difference%20to%20the%20West%E2%80%99s%20public%20affirmation%20of%20Modi%2C%20however%20indignant%20they%20may%20be%20in%20private.%20Its%20leaders%20have%20been%20perfectly%20happy%20to%20deal%20with%20him%20and%20consume%20his%20platitudes%20about%20democracy%2C%20so%20long%20as%20he%20buys%20their%20weapons%20and%20provides%20market%20access.%20And%20this%20is%20reflected%20in%20their%20reaction%20to%20Trudeau%E2%80%99s%20move.%20The%20US%20and%20Australia%20expressed%20%E2%80%9Cdeep%20concern%E2%80%9D%20about%20the%20allegation%2C%20while%20the%20UK%20Foreign%20Secretary%20James%20Cleverly%20did%20not%20name%20India%20in%20his%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FJamesCleverly%2Fstatus%2F1704160204739272930%5C%22%3Etweet%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20the%20matter.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%20%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EAll%20countries%20should%20respect%20sovereignty%20and%20the%20rule%20of%20law.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWe%20are%20in%20regular%20contact%20with%20our%20Canadian%20partners%20about%20serious%20allegations%20raised%20in%20the%20Canadian%20Parliament.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EImportant%20that%20Canada%E2%80%99s%20investigation%20runs%20its%20course%20and%20the%20perpetrators%20brought%20to%20justice.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%94%20James%20Cleverly%F0%9F%87%AC%F0%9F%87%A7%20(%40JamesCleverly)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F