he%20UK%2C%20Australia%20and%20New%20Zealand%20%E2%80%93%20and%20it%20is%20not%20inconceivable%20that%20law%20enforcement%20authorities%20in%20these%20countries%20will%20be%20together%20keeping%20an%20eye%20on%20organised%20diaspora%20activity%20and%20its%20links%20to%20Indian%20parties%20and%20government%20in%20the%20light%20of%20dramatic%20developments%20like%20these.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWestern%20governments%20will%20not%20be%20oblivious%20to%20the%20growing%20right-wing%20activism%20among%20the%20diaspora%20and%20the%20efforts%20of%20the%20BJP%20and%20the%20Modi%20government%20to%20harness%20that%20energy%20for%20political%20support%20and%20to%20stave%20off%20criticism%20of%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20West%20can%20arguably%20live%20with%20a%20measure%20of%20diaspora%20mobilization%20but%20not%20entirely%20look%20away%20when%20it%20is%20disrupting%20civil%20peace%20and%20the%20social%20climate%20in%20their%20own%20countries.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThere%20have%20been%2C%20to%20be%20sure%2C%20several%20unsavoury%20incidents%20in%20recent%20times%20involving%20Indian-origin%20immigrants.%20There%20were%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nytimes.com%2F2022%2F09%2F25%2Fnyregion%2Fbulldozer-indian-parade-new-jersey.html%5C%22%3Ebulldozers%3C%2Fa%3E%20at%20a%20parade%20in%20New%20Jersey%20that%20symbolically%20supported%20the%20demolition%20of%20Muslim%20homes%20in%20India%20by%20the%20BJP%20government.%20There%20were%20violent%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Fviolent-clashes-in-leicester-last-year-stoked-by-modis-hindu-nationalist-party-daily-mail%5C%22%3Ecommunal%20clashes%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20Leicester%2C%20the%20UK%2C%20last%20year.%20There%20were%20Sikh-Hindu%20clashes%20in%20Sydney%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.abc.net.au%2Fnews%2F2023-06-10%2Ftensions-over-khalistan-separatist-movement-boil-over-in-sydney%2F102463024%5C%22%3Ethis%20year%3C%2Fa%3E.%20And%20reports%20have%20emerged%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fcity%2Fchandigarh%2Foz-police-see-hindu-hand-in-temple-graffiti-advise-closure%2Farticleshow%2F103744961.cms%3Ffrom%3Dmdr%5C%22%3Efindings%3C%2Fa%3E%20by%20police%20in%20Queensland%20about%20the%20defacement%20of%20Hindu%20temples%20in%20Australia.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EForeign%20governments%20will%20be%20keen%20to%20assess%20if%20such%20incidents%20develop%20organically%20or%20were%20provoked%20by%20foreign%20actors.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EIntensified%20Sikh-Hindu%20schism%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ETrudeau%E2%80%99s%20statement%20is%20likely%20to%20intensify%20the%20divide%20among%20various%20Indian-origin%20diaspora%20groups.%20Sikh%20and%20other%20minority%20groups%20will%20organise%20against%20Hindu%20nationalist%20organisations%20and%20pressure%20foreign%20governments%20to%20act%20against%20them%20%E2%80%93%20the%20Hindu%20Right%20will%20counter-mobilise%20and%20lobby.%20All%20concerned%20will%20be%20in%20the%20crosshairs%20of%20Western%20bureaucratic%20interest%20and%20regulation.%20If%20Indians%20were%20to%20bring%20their%20domestic%20politics%20and%20divisions%20into%20other%20countries%2C%20it%20is%20only%20natural%20that%20governments%20of%20those%20lands%20would%20be%20more%20engaged%20in%20their%20surveillance%20of%20diaspora%20communities.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20Indian%20middle%20class%20can%20scarcely%20afford%20to%20be%20drawn%20into%20unhelpful%20transnational%20political%20projects%2C%20especially%20when%20just%20about%20every%20Western%20country%20is%20seeing%20anti-immigrant%20opinion%20on%20the%20rise.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIndians%20are%20largely%20known%20abroad%20for%20quietly%20getting%20on%20with%20their%20migrant%20lives.%20Importing%20illiberal%20norms%20and%20methods%20and%20reshaping%20the%20political%20cultures%20of%20host%20countries%20in%20undesirable%20ways%20is%20bound%20to%20provoke%20anti-immigrant%20sentiment%20that%20Indians%20have%20managed%20to%20avoid%20so%20far.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ESush