%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EA%20couple%20in%20the%20US%20said%20their%20teenage%20daughter%20discovered%20a%20hidden%20camera%20inside%20a%20bathroom%20on%20an%20American%20Airlines%20flight%20from%20Charlotte%20to%20Boston%20earlier%20this%20month%2C%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.newsweek.com%2Fteenage-girl-finds-hidden-camera-american-airlines-plane-toilet-1827625%5C%22%3E%20Newsweek%20%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fem%3Ereported.%20They%20believe%20a%20flight%20attendant%20snuck%20it%20into%20the%20bathroom%20and%20used%20it%20to%20record%20her.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20incident%20happened%20on%20September%202%20when%20the%C2%A0couple's%2014-year-old%20daughter%20was%20waiting%20to%20use%20the%20bathroom%20in%20coach.%20Soon%2C%20a%20male%20flight%20attendant%20approached%20her%20and%20told%20her%20she%20could%20instead%20use%20the%20bathroom%20in%20first%20class%2C%20as%20%26quot%3Bit'll%20be%20quicker.%26quot%3B%20As%20she%C2%A0arrived%20at%20the%20first-class%20bathroom%20the%20flight%20attendant%20stopped%20her%20and%20said%20he%20needed%20to%20go%20inside%20to%20wash%20his%20hands%20as%20garbage%20collection%20was%20about%20to%20start.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWhen%20she%20went%20inside%2C%20she%20noticed%20a%20red%20sticker%20on%20the%20inside%20of%20the%20toilet%20seat%20lid%20that%20read%2C%20%26quot%3Bseat%20broken.%26quot%3B%20The%20girl%20said%20she%20used%20the%20toilet%2C%20and%20afterward%2C%20upon%20second%20glance%2C%20she%20noticed%20there%20was%20an%20iPhone%20underneath%20the%20tape%20with%20the%20camera%20lenses%20facing%20out.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EShe%20took%20a%20picture%20of%20it%20and%20showed%20it%20to%20her%20parents%20when%20she%20got%20back%20to%20her%20seat.%20The%20picture%20showed%20a%20cellphone%20with%20the%20flash%20on%20taped%20upside%20down%20to%20the%20inside%20of%20a%20toilet%20seat%20lid.%20Concerned%2C%20her%20mother%20immediately%20went%20to%20look%20for%20the%20phone%20but%20it%20was%20gone%20by%20the%20time%20she%20reached%20the%20toilet.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAfter%20the%20girl%20headed%20back%20to%20her%20seat%2C%20the%20same%20flight%20attendant%20went%20back%20inside%20the%20bathroom%2C%20her%20parents%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20sickening.%20There%20is%20no%20doubt%20in%20our%20minds%20that%20she%20was%20targeted%20by%20him.%20I%20mean%2C%20he%20approached%20her%20while%20she%20was%20waiting%20for%20the%20bathroom.%20He%20walked%20her%20up%20there.%20He%20went%20right%20in%20before%20her%20and%20then%20right%20after%20her%2C''%20the%20girl's%20father%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20couple%20said%20their%20family%20provided%20statements%20to%20Massachusetts%20State%20Police%20investigators%20when%20they%20landed.%C2%A0The%20flight%20attendant%20was%20escorted%20off%20the%20plane%20after%20airline%20staff%20checked%20the%20bathroom%2C%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.boston25news.com%2Fnews%2Flocal%2Ffamily-says-14-year-old-daughter-discovered-phone-taped-back-toilet-seat-flight-boston%2FPPFGPIE5S5G4NPNZ4YB77UPLE4%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EBoston%2025%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0reported.%20American%20Airlines%20says%20they%20are%20cooperating%20fully%20with%20the%20investigation%2C%20which%20is%20now%20in%20the%20hands%20of%20the%20FBI.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EPaul%20T.%20Llewellyn%2C%20the%20attorney%20representing%20the%20family%2C%20told%20%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nbcboston.com%2Fnews%2Flocal%2Fpassenger-aboard-boston-bound-plane-complained-of-camera-placed-in-bathroom%2F3138271%2F%5C%22%3ENBC10%20Boston%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%20in%20a%20statement%20that%20%26quot%3Bit%20is%20shocking%20that%20a%20sexual%20predator%20could%20brazenly%20prey%20on%20a%20minor%20while%20she%20used%20the%20bathroom%20on%20a%20flight.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1695208680000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-09%2Fe99v5pgo_hidden-iphone-in-plane-toilet_625x300_20_September_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22htt