20Shah%20on%20Wednesday%20took%20a%20dig%20at%20Leader%20of%20Congress%20in%20Lok%20Sabha%20Adhir%20Ranjan%20Chowdhury%20after%20he%20interrupted%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20(BJP)%20MP%20Nishikant%20Dubey%20when%20he%20stood%20up%20to%20speak%20on%20the%20Women's%20Reservation%20Bill.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EBJP%20MP%20Nishikant%20Dubey%20stood%20up%20to%20speak%20after%20Congress%20Parliamentary%20Party%20Chairperson%20Sonia%20Gandhi's%20remarks%20on%20the%20Nari%20Shakti%20Vandan%20Adhiniam%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThere%20was%20a%20brief%20ruckus%20in%20the%20House%20as%20Adhir%20Ranjan%20Chowdhury%20and%20other%20MPs%20from%20the%20opposition%20insisted%20that%20the%20Government%20should%20have%20nominated%20a%20woman%20MP%20to%20speak.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAmit%20Shah%20intervened%20and%20took%20potshots%20at%20Adhir%20Ranjan%20Chowdhury%20for%20interrupting%20Dubey's%20speech%20and%20said%20he%20may%20be%20getting%20%26quot%3Bjealous%26quot%3B%20as%20he%20did%20not%20get%20to%20speak%20first.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20want%20to%20ask%20Adhir%20Ranjan%20ji%2C%20will%20only%20women%20care%20for%20women%2C%20can%20men%20not%20speak%20up%20for%20them%3F%20What%20kind%20of%20society%20do%20you%20want%20to%20build%3F%20Women's%20welfare%2C%20women's%20concerns...brothers%20should%20be%20a%20step%20ahead.%20That%20is%20the%20tradition%20of%20this%20country.%20Everyone%20has%20the%20right%20to%20think%20of%20women's%20welfare.%20And%20when%20Nishikant%20ji%20stood%20up%20from%20our%20side%20to%20speak%2C%20what%20was%20his%20(Chowdhury's)%20objection%3F%20Maybe%20because%20he%20didn't%20get%20the%20chance%20to%20speak%20first%2C%20he%20is%20getting%20a%20little%20jealous%2C%26quot%3B%20Amit%20Shah%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20bill%20was%20earlier%20moved%20for%20passage%20in%20the%20House%20by%20Union%20Law%20Minister%20Arjun%20Ram%20Meghwal.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20bill%20was%20introduced%20in%20Lok%20Sabha%20on%20Tuesday%2C%20the%20