community%20who%20oppose%20the%20anti-India%20agenda%E2%80%9D.%20%E2%80%9CIndian%20nationals%20are%20therefore%20advised%20to%20avoid%20travelling%20to%20regions%20and%20potential%20venues%20in%20Canada%20that%20have%20seen%20such%20incidents.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAddressing%20a%20specific%20demography%2C%20the%20advisory%20also%20asked%20Indian%20students%20%E2%80%9Cin%20particular%E2%80%9D%20to%20%E2%80%9Cexercise%20extreme%20caution%20and%20remain%20vigilant%E2%80%9D%20due%20to%20the%20%E2%80%9Cdeteriorating%20security%20environment%20in%20Canada%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIt%20also%20called%20on%20Indian%20nationals%20and%20students%20to%20register%20with%20the%20appropriate%20diplomatic%20missions%20or%20the%20%E2%80%98%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Fmadad.gov.in%2F%5C%22%3Emadad%E2%80%99%3C%2Fa%3E%20portal.%20%E2%80%9CRegistration%20would%20enable%20the%20High%20Commission%20and%20the%20Consulates%20General%20to%20better%20connect%20with%20Indian%20citizens%20in%20Canada%20in%20the%20event%20of%20any%20emergency%20or%20untoward%20incident%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20that%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EEarlier%20on%20Wednesday%2C%20some%20news%20portals%20and%20channels%2C%20including%20ANI%20and%20Times%20Now%2C%20had%20misreported%20that%20Canada%20had%20issued%20a%20new%20advisory%20against%20travel%20to%20India.%20However%2C%20as%20Alt%20News%20co-founder%20Mohammed%20Zubair%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fzoo_bear%2Fstatus%2F1704346980183630070%5C%22%3Epointed%20out%20on%20X%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Canada%20has%20been%20issuing%20much%20the%20same%20advisory%20on%20India%20for%20the%20last%20few%20years%2C%20and%20the%20developments%20of%20the%20last%20few%20days%20have%20not%20changed%20that.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIndia%E2%80%99s%20advisory%20applies%20to%20Indian%20nationals%2C%20but%20Canada%20is%20home%20to%20a%20large%20Indian%20diaspora.%20According%20to%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fabcnews.go.com%2FInternational%2FwireStory%2F