%20tit-for-tat%20expulsion%20of%20envoys%20and%20comes%20in%20the%20wake%20of%20the%20diplomatic%20stand-off%20between%20the%20countries%20following%20Canada's%20allegations%20on%20the%20involvement%20of%20Indian%20officials%20in%20the%20killing%20of%20a%20Khalistani%20terrorist.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20strong%20advisory%2C%20which%20was%20issued%20on%20Wednesday%2C%20speaks%20of%20growing%20anti-India%20activities%20and%20%26quot%3Bpolitically%20condoned%20hate%20crimes%26quot%3B%20in%20Canada%20and%20urges%20Indian%20nationals%20in%20the%20country%20-%20as%20well%20as%20those%20planning%20to%20travel%20there%20-%20to%20exercise%20caution.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20in%20the%20Canadian%20parliament%20on%20Monday%2C%20Prime%20Minister%20Justin%20Trudeau%20had%20said%20his%20government%20had%20%26quot%3Bcredible%20allegations%26quot%3B%20linking%20the%20killing%20of%20Khalistani%20terrorist%20Hardeep%20Singh%20Nijjar%20in%20June%20with%20the%20%26quot%3Bagents%20of%20the%20Government%20of%20India%26quot%3B.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20Indian%20government%20has%20rejected%20the%20claim%20as%20%26quot%3Babsurd%20and%20motivated%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E'Anti-India%20Activities'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20advisory%20released%20by%20India%20states%2C%20%26quot%3BIn%20view%20of%20growing%20anti-India%20activities%20and%20politically-condoned%20hate%20crimes%20and%20criminal%20violence%20in%20Canada%2C%20all%20Indian%20nationals%20there%20and%20those%20contemplating%20travel%20are%20urged%20to%20exercise%20utmost%20caution.%20%C2%A0Recently%2C%20threats%20have%20particularly%20targeted%20Indian%20diplomats%20and%20sections%20of%20the%20Indian%20community%20who%20oppose%20the%20anti-India%20agenda.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20communication%20urged%20Indian%20nationals%20to%20avoid%20travelling%20to%20regions%20and%20potential%20venues%20in%20Canada%20that%20have%20seen%20such%20incidents.%20It%20also%20said%20that%20the%20Indian%20High%20Commission%20and%20consulates%20general%20will%20be%20in%20contact%20with%20the%20Canadian%20authorities%20to%20%26quot%3Bensure%20the%20safety%20and%20well-being%20of%20the%20Indian%20community%20in%20Canada%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EUrging%20students%20to%20stay%20vigilant%2C%20it%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BGiven%20the%20deteriorating%20security%20environment%20in%20Canada%2C%20Indian%20students%20in%20particular%20are%20advised%20to%20exercise%20extreme%20caution%20and%20remain%20vigilant.%20Indian%20nationals%20and%20students%20from%20India%20in%20Canada%20must%20also%20register%20with%20the%20High%20Commission%20of%20India%20in%20Ottawa%20or%20Consulates%20General%20of%20India%20in%20Toronto%20and%20Vancouver%20through%20their%20respective%20websites%2C%20or%20the%20MADAD%20portal%2C%20madad.gov.in%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ERegistration%2C%20it%20added%2C%20would%20enable%20the%20High%20Commission%20and%20the%20consulates%20general%20to%20better%20connect%20with%20Indian%20citizens%20in%20Canada%20in%20%26quot%3Bthe%20event%20of%20any%20emergency%20or%20untoward%20incident%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ECanada's%20Update%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ECanada%20had%20updated%20its%20travel%20advisory%20to%20India%20on%20Tuesday%20and%20the%20new%20communication%20mirrors%2C%20to%20a%20large%20extent%2C%20what%20the%20United%20States%20advises%20its%20citizens.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EOn%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%2C%20Canada's%20advisory%20stated%2C%20%26quot%3BThe%20security%20situation%20in%20the%20Union%20Territory%20of%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20is%20tense.%20There%20are%20high%20risks%20of%20violent%20protests%2C%20civil%20unrest%20and%20acts%20of%20terrorism%20and%20militancy...%20Terrorist%20attacks%20against%20security%20forces%20have%20led%20to%20civilian%20casualties.%20Further%20attacks%20could%20take%20place%20at%20any%20time.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMentioning%20Assam%20and%20Manipur%2C%20it%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BSeveral%20extremist%20and%20insurgent%20groups%20are%20active%20in%20the%20northeastern%20states%20of%20Assam%20and%20Manipur.%20They%20regularly%20target%20local%20government%20and%20security%20forces%20and%20may%20use%20various%20criminal%20activities%20to%20finance%20their%20activities.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1695205140000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.ndtvimg.com%2Fi%2F2018-03%2Fpm-modi-justin-trudeau-pti_650x400_61519877647.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fexercise-utmost-caution-new-delhis-advisory-to-indians-in-canada-4406665%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20day%20after%20Canada%20issued%20a%20travel%20advisory%20for%20India%2C%20the%20Ministry%20Of%20External%20Affairs%20has%20also%20released%20an%20advisory%20for%20Indians%20in%20that%20country.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fexercise-utmost-caution-new-delhis-advisory-to-indians-in-canada-4406665%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fexercise-utmost-caution-new-delhis-advisory-to-indians-in-canada-4406665%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fexercise-utmost-caution-new-delhis-advisory-to-indians-in-canada-4406665%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Mohammed%20Siraj%20back%20to%20No.%201%20in%20ICC%20ODI%20rankings%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1695205092000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-103809141%2Cimgsize-59852.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fsports%2Fcricket%2Faustralia-in-india%2Fmohammed-siraj-back-to-no-1-in-icc-odi-rankings%2Farticleshow%2F103809040.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Indian%20fast%20bowler%20Mohammed%20Siraj%20has%20regained%20the%20top%20spot%20in%20the%20ICC%20ODI%20bowling%20rankings%20after%20a%20six-wicket%20performance%20in%20the%20Asia%20Cup%20final%20match%20against%20Sri%20Lanka.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20SPORTS%20DESK%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fsports%2Fcricket%2Faustralia-in-india%2Fmohammed-siraj-back-to-no-1-in-icc-odi-rankings%2Farticleshow%2F103809040.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22'Illegal'%3A%20Lawyers%20Slam%20Hyderabad%20Cops%20For%20Frisking%20People%20at%20Cafes%20as%20'Preventative%20Measure'%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F20152945%2Fsantosh.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20an%20apparent%20violation%20of%20privacy%2C%20the%20Santosh%20Nagar%20police%20in%20Hyderabad%20carried%20out%20a%20blanket%20search%20operation%20on%20September%2016%2C%20frisking%20over%20200%20customers%20in%20eateries%20under%20its%20jurisdiction.%20Police%20personnel%20frisked%20customers%20who%20were%20having%20their%20dinner%20and%20evening%20tea%2C%20and%20went%20through%20their%20pockets%20and%20wallets%2C%20as%20a%20%E2%80%9Cpreventive%20measure.%E2%80%9D%20A%20video%20of%20this%20exercise%20shows%20the%20Station%20House%20Officer%20(SHO)%20entering%20a%20food%20outlet%20and%20asking%20the%20seated%20customers%20to%20stand%20up.%20%E2%80%9CJust%20remain%20standing%2C%20you%20will%20be%20frisked%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20tells%20them%20and%20proceeds%20to%20direct%20his%20subordinates%20to%20frisk%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20search%20did%20not%20yield%20any%20results.%20Nobody%20was%20found%20with%20any%20drugs%20nor%20were%20any%20weapons%20seized.%20Santosh%20Nagar%20SHO%20P.%20Shiva%20Chandra%20told%20%3Cem%3ETNM%3C%2Fem%3E%20that%20they%20frisked%20the%20customers%20on%20suspicion%20of%20ganja%20(narcotic%20substance)%20or%20weapons%20possession.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20carried%20out%20searches%20in%2010%20eateries%20in%20our%20jurisdiction.%20We%20did%20not%20find%20anything%20in%20the%20search%2C%20but%20this%20is%20a%20preventive%20measure%20to%20stop%20any%20crime%20from%20occuring%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20lawyers%20argue%20that%20this%20arbitrary%20police%20action%20is%20illegal.%20%E2%80%9CIt%20is%20atrocious%20to%20frisk%20citizens%20and%20go%20through%20their%20things.%20If%20the%20police%20suspect%20anyone%20of%20possessing%20any%20narcotic%20substance%2C%20they%20should%20be%20accompanied%20by%20a%20gazetted%20officer%20while%20carrying%20out%20the%20search.%20And%20before%20the%20search%20begins%2C%20the%20gazetted%20officer%20should%20thoroughly%20check%20the%20police%20personnel%20so%20that%20they%20do%20not%20plant%20any%20incriminating%20material%20on%20any%20suspect%20and%20frame%20them%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20lawyer%20and%20president%20of%20Human%20Rights%20Forum%20(HRF)%2C%20G.%20Madhava%20Rao.%20HRF%20is%20a%20civil%20rights%20organisation.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CCarrying%20out%20such%20a%20search%20in%20the%20absence%20of%20a%20gazetted%20officer%20is%20illegal%2C%E2%80%9D%20Rao%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESearches%20carried%20out%20in%20poor%20localities%20has%20also%20raised%20concerns%20of%20the%20police%E2%80%99s%20inherent%20bias%20against%20certain%20communities.%20For%20instance%2C%20Santosh%20Nagar%20is%20a%20Muslim-dominated%20area.%20And%20the%20police%20admit%20to%20profiling%20suspects%20based%20on%20their%20looks%2C%20attire%2C%20and%20vehicle.%20%E2%80%9CThis%20is%20not%20the%20first%20time%20we%20are%20carrying%20out%20such%20a%20task.%20In%20our%20jurisdiction%2C%20we%20have%20a%20problem%20of%20ganja%20possession%20and%20other%20criminal%20activities.%20During%20vehicle%20checks%2C%20we%20regularly%20frisk%20suspects%20to%20search%20for%20ganja.%20We%20do%20fingerprint%20scanning%20and%20facial%20recognition%20of%20these%20suspects%20to%20check%20if%20they%20have%20any%20criminal%20background%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20SHO%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThis%20form%20of%20policing%20was%20previously%20slammed%20by%20many%20civil%20rights%20activists.%20In%20%3Cins%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thenewsminute.com%2Ftelangana%2Fhyderabad-cops-are-illegally-checking-phones-whatsapp-citizens-part-drug-crackdown-156997%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E2021%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%20the%20Hyderabad%20police%20faced%20severe%20backlash%20when%20they%20started%20checking%20phones%20and%20the%20WhatsApp%20history%20of%20people%20randomly%20to%20identify%20potential%20ganja%20addicts%20and%20sellers.%C2%A0%20These%20type%20of%20searches%20are%20still%20happening%20in%20the%20areas%20around%20Dhoolpet%2C%20Mangalhat%2C%20Bhoiguda%20Kaman%2C%20and%20Jumeraat%20Bazaar%2C%20etc.%20Protesting%20this%20extreme%20form%20of%20illegal%20policing%2C%20the%20%3Cins%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thenewsminute.com%2Ftelangana%2Fhyd-police-commissioner-sent-legal-notice-over-random-whatsapp-checks-drugs-157073%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EInternet%20Freedom%20Foundation%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3C%2Fins%3Ehad%20previously%20issued%20a%20legal%20notice%20to%20the%20then%20Hyderabad%20police%20commissioner%20and%20present%20state%20Director%20General%20of%20Police%2C%20Anjani%20Kumar.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ETNM%20has%20%3Cins%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thenewsminute.com%2Ftopic%2Ftelangana-surveillance%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ereported%20extensively%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%20about%20controversial%20police%20exercises%2C%20including%20cordon%20and%20search%2C%20which%20are%20justified%20as%20%E2%80%98preemptive%20measures%E2%80%99%20to%20prevent%20crime.%20The%20cordon%20and%20search%20operation%20involves%20blocking%20off%20an%20area%2C%20usually%20slums%20or%20localities%20that%20house%20poor%20people%2C%20and%20check%20for%20their%20Aadhaar%20card%2C%20gas%20cylinder%20and%20vehicle%20documents.%20Previously%20restricted%20to%20searches%20by%20the%20Army%20in%20conflict%20zones%2C%20this%20operation%20has%20now%20spread%20to%20states%20like%20Telanagna%2C%20Andhra%20Pradesh%2C%20and%20Tamil%20Nadu.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CFrisking%20people%20randomly%20is%20completely%20illegal.%20There%20should%20be%20some%20credible%20suspicion%20if%20such%20an%20action%20is%20being%20carried%20out.%20There%20has%20to%20be%20an%20FIR%20or%20a%20case%20registered%20in%20the%20police%E2%80%99s%20General%20Diary.%20Without%20any%20credible%20evidence%2C%20searching%20people%20randomly%20is%20illegal%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20lawyer%20Vasudha%20Nagaraj.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20eateries%20that%20were%20searched%20on%20September%2016%20include%20King%20Khaja%20Hotel%2C%20Lucky%20Hotel%2C%20Hafeez%20Cafe%2C%20Mashallah%20Hotel%2C%20among%20others.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20SHO%20Shiva%20Chandra%2C%20Santosh%20Nagar%2C%20which%20is%20a%20Muslim-populated%20area%2C%20has%20a%20problem%20with%20drugs%20and%20other%20criminal%20activities.%20%E2%80%9CThere%20are%20%E2%80%98roadside%20romeos%E2%80%99%2C%20and%20a%20lot%20of%20suspects%20who%20sit%20in%20these%20eateries%20till%20late%20at%20night%20and%20plan%20crimes%20such%20as%20murder%2C%20smuggling%2C%20and%20other%20nefarious%20activities%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%20The%20policing%20is%20carried%20out%20only%20in%20the%20evenings%20and%20nights%20when%20there%20is%20heavy%20activity%2C%20he%20revealed.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thenewsminute.com%2Fpartner%2Fchildhood-cancer-why-advanced-paediatric-oncology-centres-are-key-to-saving-lives%5C%22%3Earticle%3C%2Fa%3E%20was%20originally%20published%20by%3C%2Fem%3E%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thenewsminute.com%2F%5C%22%3EThe%20News%20Minute%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1695204930000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F20152945%2Fsantosh.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fright