Sonia%20Gandhi%20won%E2%80%99t%20slam%20China%3F%E2%80%9D.%20Republic%20TV%E2%80%99s%20main%20debates%20on%20June%2019%20were%20headlined%3A%20%E2%80%9CUnarmed%20with%20fact%2C%20Congress%20insults%20Army%E2%80%9D%3B%20%E2%80%9CIs%20there%20a%20%E2%80%98special%20relation%E2%80%99%20between%20the%20Congress%20and%20China%3F%E2%80%9D%20and%20%E2%80%9CPeople%E2%80%99s%20movement%20against%20China%20gets%20bigger%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20371px)%2085vw%2C%20371px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2021%2F11%2F12100436%2FIMG_0050-1-300x208.png%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22371%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2021%2F11%2F12100436%2FIMG_0050-1-300x208.png%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2021%2F11%2F12100436%2FIMG_0050-1-1024x711.png%201024w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2021%2F11%2F12100436%2FIMG_0050-1.png%201200w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-563875%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22257%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EPrice%20of%20the%20Modi%20Years%20by%20Aakar%20Patel.%20%3C%2Fem%3EWestland%20(2021).%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3EFor%20my%20book%3Cem%3E%2C%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Cem%3EPrice%20of%20the%20Modi%20Years%2C%3C%2Fem%3E%20which%20is%20being%20republished%20this%20month%20in%20paperback%2C%20I%20looked%20at%20the%20two%20top%20English%20news%20channels.%20What%20were%20the%20subjects%20of%20their%20prime-time%20debates%20in%20this%20period%20when%20there%20was%20the%20Chinese%20intrusion%20and%20the%20economy%20was%20contracting%20because%20of%20the%20Covid-19%20lockdown%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20months%20of%20May%2C%20June%20and%20July%2C%20Times%20Now%20had%2033%20prime-time%20debates%20which%20criticised%20the%20opposition%E2%80%99s%20actions.%20It%20had%20none%20that%20criticised%20the%20Narendra%20Modi%20government.%20There%20were%20zero%20debates%20on%20the%20economic%20recession.%20In%20the%20same%20three%20months%2C%20Republic%20TV%20had%2047%20debates%20that%20criticised%20the%20opposition%E2%80%99s%20actions.%20It%20had%20none%20that%20criticised%20the%20Modi%20government%E2%80%99s%20actions%20and%20none%20on%20the%20economic%20recession.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThis%20was%20a%20period%20in%20which%20between%20June%207%20and%20June%2027%2C%20the%20price%20of%20petrol%2Fdiesel%20was%20hiked%20every%20single%20day%20for%2021%20days.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EOn%20June%2016%2C%20India%20announced%20that%20it%20had%20lost%2020%20soldiers%2C%20who%20were%20bludgeoned%20to%20death%20in%20hand-to-hand%20combat%20with%20the%20Chinese%20in%20the%20Galwan%20Valley%20in%20Ladakh.%20Daily%20Covid%20infections%20rose%20from%202%2C300%20cases%20on%20May%201%20to%20over%2057%2C000%20daily%20cases%20on%20July%2031.%20But%20note%20the%20focus%20of%20the%20%E2%80%9Cdebates%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EA%20few%20days%20later%2C%20the%20%3Cem%3EIndian%20Journalism%20Review%3C%2Fem%3E%20published%20another%20note%20that%20the%20PMO%20had%20circulated%20to%20the%20television%20channels%2C%20instructing%20them%20on%20what%20to%20focus%20on.%20The%20note%20read%2C%20%E2%80%9CModi%20effect%20loud%20and%20clear.%20Taming%20expansionist%20China%20is%20a%20Herculean%20task%20but%20the%20right%20strategies%20and%20actions%20can%20yield%20to%20(sic)%20outstanding%20results.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EChina%20hasn%E2%80%99t%20pulled%20back.%20China%20has%20been%20pushed%20back%2C%20by%20a%20united%20nation%20led%20by%20a%20leader%20who%20led%20from%20the%20front.%20By%20taking%20decisive%20military%2C%20economic%20and%20strategic%20moves%2C%20PM%20Modi%20has%20pushed%20back%20China.%20The%20notion%20of%20economic%20infallibility%20of%20China%20has%20received%20a%20tight%20slap%20with%20the%20PM%E2%80%99s%20clarion%20call%20of%20Atma%20Nirbhar%20Bharat%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EWatch%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fmedia%2Ffull-text-n-ram-on-india-blocs-tv-anchor-boycott-list-and-state-of-journalism%5C%22%3EFull%20Text%20%7C%20N%20Ram%20on%20INDIA%20Bloc%E2%80%99s%20TV%20Anchor%20Boycott%20List%20and%20State%20of%20Journalism%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ETimes%20Now%20responded%20with%20debates%20headlined%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%98PM%20Modi%20punishes%20Expansionist%20China%2C%20doubters%20put%20to%20shame%3F%E2%80%99%3Cbr%3E%20%E2%80%98China%20admits%20it%20was%20pushed%20back%2C%20will%20Army%20doubters%20surrender%3F%E2%80%99%3Cbr%3E%20%E2%80%98China%20admits%20push%20back%20but%20lobby%20continues%20to%20lie%3F%E2%80%99%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAnd%20Republic%20TV%20with%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%98Prime%20Minister%20leads%20from%20the%20front%E2%80%99%3Cbr%3E%20%E2%80%98PM%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20strong%20leadership%20pushes%20back%20China%E2%80%99%3Cbr%3E%20%E2%80%98Ladakh%20reality%20check%3A%20Galwan%20victory%20a%20slap%20in%20lobby%E2%80%99s%20face%E2%80%99.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EOthers%20have%20looked%20at%20the%20data%20and%20arrived%20at%20similar%20numbers.%20In%20a%20study%20published%20at%20the%20end%20of%202020%2C%20political%20scientist%20Christophe%20Jaffrelot%20and%20data%20analyst%20Vihang%20Jumle%20examined%20Republic%20TV%E2%80%99s%20content.%20They%20wrote%20in%20%3Cem%3ECaravan%3C%2Fem%3E%20magazine%2C%20%E2%80%9CWe%20studied%20all%20prime-time%20debates%20held%20since%20the%20channel%20was%20launched%20in%20May%202017%2C%20until%20April%202020%2C%20when%20we%20began%20the%20study%20%E2%80%94%201%2C779%20in%20all.%20Our%20conclusion%20was%20clear%3A%20Republic%20TV%E2%80%99s%20debates%20have%20been%20consistently%20biased%20in%20favour%20of%20the%20Modi%20government%20and%20its%20policies%2C%20as%20well%20as%20the%20ideology%20of%20the%20BJP.%20What%E2%80%99s%20worse%2C%20these%20debates%20have%20rarely%20featured%20some%20of%20the%20most%20pressing%20issues%20that%20impact%20Indians%2C%20such%20as%20the%20state%20of%20the%20economy%2C%20education%20or%20health.%20Instead%2C%20they%20have%20consisted%20mostly%20of%20attacks%20against%20the%20Opposition%20as%20well%20as%20any%20groups%20or%20persons%20that%20oppose%20the%20ruling%20government%E2%80%99s%20ideology.%20%E2%80%9CSome%20figures%20are%20staggering%2C%20if%20unsurprising.%20Nearly%20fifty%20per%20cent%20of%20Republic%20TV%E2%80%99s%20political%20debates%20criticised%20the%20Opposition%2C%20but%20it%20has%20not%20conducted%20even%20one%20debate%20that%20we%20could%20classify%20as%20being%20in%20the%20Opposition%E2%80%99s%20favour.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ETo%20return%20to%20the%20question%20we%20began%20with%20%E2%80%93%20what%20is%20the%20evidence%20we%20have%20to%20suggest%20that%20some%20anchors%20and%20TV%20stations%20act%20as%20extensions%20of%20the%20government%3F%20The%20evidence%20is%20quite%20clear%20for%20anyone%20who%20wants%20to%20seek%20it.%20There%20is%20absolutely%20no%20question%20that%20the%20opposition%20is%20correct%20in%20having%20concluded%20that%20it%20is%20being%20asked%20to%20play%20a%20rigged%20game%20by%20large%20sections%20of%20the%20media.%20It%20has%20every%20right%20to%20refuse%20to%20be%20any%20part%20of%20this.%20One%20hopes%2C%20though%20one%20is%20not%20optimistic%2C%20that%20this%20action%20to%20some%20extent%20corrects%20the%20lunacy%20which%20has%20infected%20our%20national%20media%20and%20has%20damaged%20our%20nation.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EAakar%20Patel%20is%20a%20senior%20journalist%20and%20columnist.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1695200400000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F01145303%2FWhatsApp-Image-2023-09-01-at-1.39.00-PM-1.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fwhy-the-india-alliance-is-right-in-boycotting-pro-government-media%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22In%20the%20months%20of%20May%2C%20June%20and%20July%2C%20Times%20Now%20had%2033%20prime-time%20debates%20which%20criticised%20the%20opposition%E2%80%99s%20actions.%20It%20had%20none%20that%20criticised%20the%20Narendra%20Modi%20government.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fwhy-the-india-alliance-is-right-in-boycotting-pro-government-media%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Watch%3A%20'Dil%20Jashn%20Bole'%20-%20ICC%20unveils%20ODI%20WC's%20official%20anthem%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1695200058000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-103806160%2Cimgsize-59052.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fsports%2Fcricket%2Ficc-world-cup%2Fdil-jashn-bole-icc-unveils-odi-world-cups-official-anthem%2Farticleshow%2F103806110.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20ICC%20Men's%20Cricket%20World%20Cup%202023%20on%20Wednesday%20released%20the%20official%20anthem%2C%20'Dil%20Jashn%20Bole'%2C%20a%20collaboration%20between%20actor%20Ranveer%20Singh%20and%20Bollywood%20composer%20Pritam.%20The%20musical%20journey%20promises%20to%20enchant%20fans%2C%20blending%20traditional%20Indian%20instruments%20with%20an%20international%20flair.%20The%20anthem%20aims%20to%20capture%20the%20emotions%20and%20fervour%20of%20the%20global%20cricket%20community.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20SPORTS%20DESK%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A23%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fsports%2Fcricket%2Ficc-world-cup%2Fdil-jashn-bole-icc-unveils-odi-world-cups-official-anthem%2Farticleshow%2F103806110.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Jadavpur%20University's%20Failure%20to%20Check%20Ragging%20Menace%20Led%20to%20Student's%20Death%3A%20Probe%20Panel%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F12142242%2FScreenshot-2023-08-12-at-2.16.26.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3EThe%20internal%20committee%20of%20Jadavpur%20University%2C%20which%20was%20constituted%20to%20look%20into%20incidents%20that%20led%20to%20the%20death%20of%20a%2017-year-old%20student%20on%20the%20campus%2C%20has%20concluded%20that%20it%20was%20a%20result%20of%20an%20endemic%20ragging%20culture%20and%20failure%20on%20the%20part%20of%20authorities%20to%20check%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20report%20of%20the%20internal%20committee%20has%20noted%20that%20the%20student%20was%20made%20to%20run%20naked%20in%20front%20of%20fellow%20students%2C%20was%20labelled%20as%20%E2%80%9Cgay%E2%80%9D%2C%20and%20was%20sexually%20abused%20before%20he%20allegedly%20fell%20off%20from%20the%20second%20floor%20of%20his%20hostel%20building%20leading%20to%20his%20death%20on%20August%2010%2C%20%3Cem%3EIndian%20Express%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Fcities%2Fkolkata%2Fjadavpur-university-student-death-ragging-incident-ju-authority-ju-student-death-panel-8947604%2F%5C%22%3Ereported%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20incident%20has%20sparked%20widespread%20outrage%20across%20the%20country%2C%20particularly%20in%20West%20Bengal.%20A%20total%20of%2012%20current%20and%20former%20students%20were%20arrested%20following%20a%20murder%20case%20filed%20by%20the%20police%20based%20on%20the%20complaint%20of%20the%20deceased%20student%E2%80%99s%20father.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20university%E2%80%99s%20probe%20committee%2C%2035%20senior%20students%20and%20six%20alumni%2Funauthorised%20boarders%20were%20%E2%80%9Cinvolved%20in%20ragging%E2%80%9D%20at%20the%20main%20hostel%20of%20the%20university.%20It%20identified%20four%20senior%20students%20and%20six%20former%20students%20as%20%E2%80%9Cmain%20raggers%E2%80%9D%20which%20led%20to%20the%20death%20of%20the%20first-year%20student.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CFrom%20a%20close%20investigation%20of%20the%20issue%2C%20the%20committee%20is%20of%20the%20view%20that%20the%20victim%20was%20ragged%20in%20isolation%20(away%20from%20his%20batchmates)%20by%20a%20group%20of%20seniors%20and%20ex-students%20on%20the%20night%20of%209th%20August%20and%20was%20severely%20abused%20sexually%20too%20%5Bas%20is%20evidently%20found%20him%20being%20paraded%20naked%20amidst%20a%20mob%20of%20seniors%3B%20and%20also%20vehemently%20protesting%20against%20being%20labelled%20a%20gay)%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20committee%E2%80%99s%20report%20concluded.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fjadavpur-university-ragging-death-swapnadeep-kundu%5C%22%3EJU%20First%20Year%20Student%E2%80%99s%20%E2%80%98Ragging%E2%80%99%20Death%20Draws%20Attention%20to%20Systemic%20Flaws%20and%20Discrimination%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWhile%20noting%20it%20does%20not%20have%20%E2%80%9Cconclusive%20evidence%E2%80%9D%20on%20how%20the%20student%20fell%20from%20the%20top%20floor%2C%20the%20committee%2C%20however%2C%20identified%20two%20possibilities%3A%20%E2%80%9CA%20case%20of%20abetted%20incident%E2%80%9D%20and%20%E2%80%9CA%20case%20of%20homicide%E2%80%9D.%20The%20committee%20cautioned%20that%20the%20identified%20possibilities%20should%20not%20be%20treated%20as%20%E2%80%9Cexhaustive%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20probe%20panel%2C%20in%20its%20report%2C%20provides%20a%20blow-by-blow%20account%20of%20what%20had%20happened%20before%20the%20student%20fatally%20fell%20from%20his%20hostel%20building%20on%20August%209.%20Around%207%3A30%20pm%20that%20day%2C%20the%20victim%20was%20taken%20to%20Room%20No%3A%2059%20of%20the%20hostel%E2%80%99s%20A-2%20block%20together%20with%20a%20few%20other%20%E2%80%98fresher%E2%80%99%20students%20by%20seniors.%20They%20were%20then%20forced%20to%20shout%20%E2%80%9Chighly%20objectionable%2C%20sexist%2C%20and%20abusive%20lines%E2%80%9D%20at%20the%20women%20residents%20of%20Police%20Quarters%20next%20to%20the%20hostel.%20The%20victim%20was%20pressured%20into%20falling%20in%20line%20by%20seniors%20after%20he%20initially%20refused%20to%20utter%20such%20language.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20harassment%20by%20seniors%2C%20at%20this%20stage%2C%20%E2%80%9Cliterally%20shattered%E2%80%9D%20him%20and%20the%20deceased%20student%20broke%20into%20tears%2C%20the%20report%20notes.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20seniors%20further%20intimidated%20the%20victim%20by%20stating%20that%20police%20would%20take%20action%20against%20the%20victim%20for%20his%20utterances%20of%20such%20abusive%20words%20towards%20their%20quarters.%20At%20this%20point%2C%20the%20victim%20got%20very%20scared%20and%20started%20crying.%20Almost%20simultaneously%2C%20he%20felt%20a%20sheer%20bout%20of%20stomach%20pain%20and%20sat%20down%20clutching%20his%20abdomen.%20He%20was%20then%20given%20an%20antacid%20tablet%20by%20a%20senior%2C%20and%20then%20singularly%20led%20away%20by%20few%20seniors%20to%20another%20room%E2%80%A6%E2%80%9D%20the%20report%20read.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20committee%20then%20goes%20on%20to%20add%20that%20the%20victim%20was%20sweating%20profusely%20due%20to%20mental%20stress%20around%208%3A20%20pm%20when%20he%20was%20in%20the%20dining%20hall%20for%20dinner.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EBased%20on%20the%20students%20who%20deposed%20before%20the%20committee%2C%20it%20concluded%20that%20the%20victim%20was%20sweating%20profusely%20due%20to%20tremendous%20pressure%20from%20seniors%2C%20and%20that%20they%20were%20drinking%20heavily%20in%20his%20room.%20The%20committee%20also%20recorded%20statements%20of%20other%20students%20in%20the%20same%20hostel%20who%20smelled%20a%20strong%20odour%20of%20alcohol%20emanating%20from%20his%20room.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWhile%20he%20was%20taken%20along%20with%20other%20first-year%20students%20on%20the%20same%20night%2C%20between%209%20pm%20and%2010%3A45%20pm%2C%20to%20A-2%20block%20for%20ragging%2C%20he%20was%20soon%20singled%20out%20for%20%E2%80%9Csevere%20ragging%E2%80%9D%2C%20which%2C%20the%20committee%20notes%2C%20was%20carried%20out%20in%20a%20systematic%20and%20planned%20manner.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CA%20few%20depositors%20(deponents)%20reported%20that%20they%20heard%20a%20howling%20noise%20from%20the%20second%20floor%20of%20the%20A-2%20block.%20At%20past%2011.30%20pm%2C%20one%20of%20the%20depositors%20(deponents)%20reported%20to%20have%20heard%20a%20loud%20cry%20out%20(for%20help)%20by%20a%20single%20person%20from%20the%20second%20floor%20of%20the%20A-2%20block.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20the%20boarders%2C%20on%20hearing%20the%20loud%20cry%20went%20sprinting%20to%20the%20second-floor%20corridor%20of%20A-2%20block%2C%20and%20reported%20to%20have%20seen%20victim%20running%20in%20a%20completely%20naked%20state%2C%20and%20desperately%20trying%20to%20enter%20the%20toilet%20of%20the%20second%20floor%20of%20A-2%20block%2C%20and%20then%20rushing%20into%20room%20no.%2065.%20Even%20as%20the%20victim%20tried%20to%20close%20the%20door%20of%20room%20no.%2065%20from%20inside%2C%20seniors%20pushed%20open%20the%20door%20and%20pulled%20him%20out.%20Thereafter%2C%20he%20was%20reportedly%20offered%20a%20bottle%20of%20water%2C%20which%20he%20gulped%20a%20bit%2C%20and%20then%20threw%20the%20bottle%20at%20a%20senior%2C%20all%20the%20while%20standing%20stark%20naked%20in%20front%20of%20many%20seniors%20in%20the%20second-floor%20well-lit%20lobby%2C%20facing%20utter%20humiliation%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20report%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20committee%20then%20goes%20on%20to%20add%20that%20the%20victim%20desperately%20ran%20in%20the%20corridor%20of%20the%20second%20floor%20of%20the%20A-2%20block%20naked%20as%20around%2020%20seniors%20and%20alumni%20looked%20at%20him.%20%E2%80%9CThere%20was%20a%20large%20mob%20of%20seniors%20present%20there%20in%20both%20upper%20and%20lower%20staircases%2C%20thereby%20incidentally%20blocking%20any%20escape%20route%20for%20the%20hapless%20victim%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20committee%20notes.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20panel%2C%20however%2C%20underlines%20that%20the%20information%20on%20how%20the%20victim%20fell%20to%20the%20ground%20from%20the%20top%20floor%20is%20%E2%80%9Cuncertain%20and%20vague%E2%80%9D.%20%E2%80%9CInformation%20regarding%20the%20victim%E2%80%99s%20subsequent%20movements%2C%20just%20prior%20to%20his%20fatal%20fall%2C%20and%20eventual%20fall%2C%20is%20rather%20uncertain%20and%20vague%2C%20as%20none%20of%20the%20depositors%20(deponents)%20gave%20a%20clear-cut%20description%20of%20the%20%E2%80%98fall%E2%80%99%20incident%2C%20which%20could%20help%20in%20ascertaining%20the%20cause%20and%20sequence%20of%20the%20mishap.%20Many%20have%20reported%20to%20have%20seen%20the%20victim%20run%20towards%20the%20end%20of%20the%20corridor%20with%20a%20senior%20following%20him%2C%20but%20thereafter%2C%20the%20depositors%20(deponents)%20seem%20to%20have%20lost%20sight%20of%20the%20%E2%80%98final%20fall%E2%80%99%20due%20to%20one%20reason%20or%20the%20other%E2%80%A6%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20report%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAfter%20the%20student%20fell%2C%20the%20accused%20cleaned%20the%20blood%20stains%20with%20water%20and%20tried%20to%20suppress%20facts%20and%20remove%20evidence%2C%20the%20committee%20alleged.%20The%20senior%20students%20also%20called%20a%20number%20of%20meetings%20with%20hostellers%20in%20the%20aftermath%20of%20the%20incident%20to%20decide%20on%20the%20narrative%20they%20would%20present%20to%20the%20police%20and%20media%2C%20and%20that%20nobody%20would%20present%20any%20other%20version%2C%20the%20committee%20said%20in%20its%20report.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20probe%20panel%20also%20said%20that%20hostel%20superintendents%20deposed%20before%20it%20alleging%20a%20number%20of%20instances%20when%20they%20were%20harassed%20by%20seniors%20and%20illegal%20boarders%20in%20the%20hostel.%20No%20action%20was%20taken%20by%20the%20university%20administration%20even%20after%20they%20had%20lodged%20a%20complaint%20against%20students%20who%20harassed%20them%2C%20the%20hostel%20superintendents%20told%20the%20probe%20committee.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1695199404000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%