.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F20130238%2FF6ZXiivWMAEyYE1.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20A%20young%20man%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20accused%20of%20murder%20was%20shot%20dead%20by%20the%20police%20on%20the%20evening%20of%20September%2019%20after%20he%20allegedly%20fled%20from%20police%20custody%20when%20the%20vehicle%20he%20was%20being%20escorted%20in%20lost%20balance%20and%20came%20to%20a%20halt%20to%20avoid%20hitting%20stray%20cattle%20on%20the%20road.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20sequence%20of%20events%20in%20the%20alleged%20exchange%20of%20fire%20bring%20back%20chilling%20imageries%20of%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fvikas-dubey-killed-encounter-uttar-pradesh%5C%22%3Ekilling%20of%20Kanpur%20gangster%20Vikas%20Dubey%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20who%20along%20with%20his%20aides%20had%20been%20accused%20of%20shooting%20dead%20eight%20policemen%20in%20an%20ambush%20in%20Bikru%20village%20in%20July%202020.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20latest%20incident%20happened%20in%20Shahjahanpur%20district%20of%20UP.%20On%20Tuesday%20(September%2019)%20morning%2C%20some%20miscreants%20entered%20the%20house%20of%20one%20Alok%20Gupta%2C%20a%20trader%20and%20assistant%20professor%2C%20in%20Katra%20area%20of%20the%20city%20with%20the%20intent%20to%20carry%20out%20a%20robbery%2C%20said%20police.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWhen%20the%20Gupta%20family%20resisted%2C%20the%20suspects%20stabbed%20them%20with%20knives%2C%20said%20Shahjahanpur%20Superintendent%20of%20Police%20Ashok%20Kumar%20Meena.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20injured%20family%20members%20were%20sent%20for%20medical%20treatment%20to%20neighbouring%20Bareilly%20district%20where%20Alok%20Gupta%20succumbed%20to%20his%20injuries.%20The%20other%20family%20members%20are%20still%20receiving%20treatment.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20murder%20caused%20huge%20anger%20among%20locals%2C%20in%20particular%20the%20trading%20community%20who%20turned%20up%20at%20the%20Gupta%20residence%20in%20large%20numbers%20and%20demanded%20action%20from%20the%20police.%20The%20local%20traders%E2%80%99%20union%20threatened%20to%20shut%20all%20the%20shops%20in%20the%20kasba.%20The%20Inspector%20General%20of%20Police%2C%20Bareilly%2C%20Rakesh%20Singh%2C%20too%20reached%20the%20site%20of%20the%20crime%20and%20promised%20the%20strictest%20action%20against%20those%20who%20committed%20the%20murder.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESP%20Meena%20said%20an%20FIR%20was%20lodged%20against%20two%20named%20accused%20and%20other%20unknown%20persons%20on%20the%20complaint%20of%20the%20Gupta%20family.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22US%20Law%20Firm%20Seeks%20Action%20Against%20Adityanath%2C%20UP%20Top%20Cops%20for%20%E2%80%98Encounter%E2%80%99%20Killings%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fus-law-firm-seeks-action-against-adityanath-up-top-cops-for-encounter-killings%5C%22%3EUS%20Law%20Firm%20Seeks%20Action%20Against%20Adityanath%2C%20UP%20Top%20Cops%20for%20%E2%80%98Encounter%E2%80%99%20Killings%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EFollowing%20this%2C%20police%20said%20they%20arrested%20one%20suspect%20Shahbaz%2C%20a%20resident%20of%20mohalla%20sarai%20in%20Katra.%20The%20murder%20weapon%20was%20also%20recovered%20on%20his%20cue%2C%20said%20Meena.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EShahbaz%20was%20being%20escorted%20to%20be%20produced%20in%20court%20after%20medical%20examination%20in%20the%20evening%2C%20when%20%E2%80%9Csome%20%3Cem%3Epashu%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%9D%20(stray%20animal)%20came%20in%20front%20of%20the%20police%20jeep%20on%20a%20highway%20near%20Batlaiya%20village%20causing%20it%20to%20lose%20balance%2C%20said%20Meena.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9C%E2%80%A6the%20jeep%20became%20disbalanced%20and%20came%20to%20a%20halt.%20Making%20use%20of%20the%20situation%2C%20he%20snatched%20a%20pistol%20from%20the%20police%20inspector%20and%20jumped%20out%20%5Bof%20the%20vehicle%5D.%20He%20ran%20into%20the%20fields%20and%20started%20firing%20at%20the%20police%20from%20there%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Meena.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EPolice%20reinforcements%20were%20called%20in%20and%20repeated%20warnings%20were%20issued%20to%20Shahbaz%20asking%20him%20to%20surrender%20but%20he%20continued%20to%20fire%20at%20the%20police%2C%20said%20Meena.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20police%20also%20fired%20back%20in%20self-defence%20and%20retaliation%2C%20in%20which%20Shahbaz%20got%20injured%2C%20said%20the%20SP.%20Shahbaz%20was%20taken%20to%20a%20community%20health%20centre%20where%20doctors%20declared%20him%20brought%20dead%2C%20said%20police.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20SP%20also%20announced%20that%20the%20team%2C%20which%20was%20led%20by%20a%20circle%20officer%2C%20that%20carried%20out%20this%20%E2%80%9C%3Cem%3Esarahaniya%20karya%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%9D%20(commendable%20work)%20would%20receive%20a%20reward%20of%20Rs%2025%2C000%20from%20the%20district%20police%20and%20Rs%2050%2C000%20from%20the%20state%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20morning%20of%20July%2010%2C%202020%2C%20a%20day%20after%20he%20was%20arrested%20near%20a%20temple%20in%20Ujjain%2C%20Vikas%20Dubey%20was%20gunned%20down%20by%20the%20police%20while%20allegedly%20trying%20to%20flee%20from%20custody%20after%20an%20accident%20as%20he%20was%20being%20taken%20from%20the%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20city%20to%20Kanpur.%20This%20was%20days%20after%20Dubey%E2%80%99s%20men%20gunned%20down%20eight%20policemen%2C%20including%20a%20deputy%20SP-rank%20officer%2C%20and%20left%20seven%20others%20injured%20when%20a%20police%20team%20had%20gone%20to%20the%20village%20to%20conduct%20a%20raid.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Encouraging%20Police%20'Encounters'%20Will%20Lead%20to%20Arbitrary%20State%20Action%3A%20Former%20SC%20Judge%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fhyderabad-encounter-arbitrary-state-action-justice-chelameswar-summary-justice%5C%22%3EEncouraging%20Police%20%E2%80%98Encounters%E2%80%99%20Will%20Lead%20to%20Arbitrary%20State%20Action%3A%20Forme