-s-Shiyan-6-research-ship-sails-for-expedition-in-Indian-Ocean-1n0zYHpBtNC%2Findex.html%5C%22%3Ea%20statement%20published%20by%20the%20Chinese%20state%20broadcaster%20CGTN%20said%3C%2Fa%3E%20the%20ship%20would%20help%20%E2%80%9Cstrengthen%20scientific%20research%20cooperation%20and%20exchanges%20with%20countries%20along%20the%20Maritime%20Silk%20Road%20and%20further%20realise%20the%20integration%20of%20science%20and%20education%20for%20Belt%20and%20Road%20Initiative%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.newsfirst.lk%2F2023%2F9%2F18%2Fchina-s-shi-yan-6-heading-to-sri-lanka-pending-clearance%5C%22%3ESri%20Lanka%E2%80%99s%20%3Cem%3ENewsFirst%3C%2Fem%3E%20cites%20international%20maritime%20tracking%20data%3C%2Fa%3E%20as%20demonstrating%20that%20the%20Chinese%20geophysical%20scientific%20research%20vessel%20%3Cem%3EShi%20Yan%206%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20which%20has%20also%20attracted%20India%E2%80%99s%20attention%2C%20will%20reach%20the%20port%20of%20Colombo%20on%20September%2029.%20Last%20month%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.adaderana.lk%2Fnews.php%3Fnid%3D92959%5C%22%3Eanother%20Sri%20Lankan%20news%20portal%3C%2Fa%3E%20had%20reported%20that%20the%20Sri%20Lankan%20Ministry%20of%20Defence%20had%20%E2%80%9Cgranted%20approval%20for%20the%20Chinese%20geophysical%20and%20seismic%20survey%20vessel%20%E2%80%98Shi%20Yan%206%E2%80%99%20to%20carry%20out%20research%20on%20Sri%20Lankan%20waters%20with%20the%20National%20Aquatic%20Resources%20Research%20and%20Development%20Agency%20(NARA).%E2%80%9D%20A%20Spokesman%20of%20the%20Ministry%20of%20Defence%20was%20quoted%20as%20saying%20that%20the%20approval%20was%20granted%20on%20request%20by%20NARA%20and%20the%20Foreign%20Ministry.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fnavbharattimes.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fasian-countries%2Fsri-lanka-clears-docking-of-chinese-research-ship-shi-yan-6-at-colombo-india-us-raised-security-concerns%2Farticleshow%2F103778141.cms%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3ENavbharat%20Time