0faced%20no%20issues%20while%20using%20them.%20The%20compost%20we%20generate%20is%20used%20for%20landscaping%20purposes%20on%20our%20property.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20Deepak%20Setty%2C%20a%20senior%20manager%20overseeing%20procurement%20and%20contracts%20at%20Address%20Maker%2C%20a%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F296793%2Fex-army-officer-restores-stormwater-drains-bengaluru-rains-floods-water-logging-solution%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBengaluru-based%3C%2Fa%3E%20real%20estate%20company%2C%20says%2C%C2%A0%20%E2%80%9CFor%20each%20residential%20project%2C%20we%20require%20one%20organic%20waste%20composter%20and%20we%20do%20about%20two%20to%20three%20projects%20a%20year.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CFor%20about%20eight%20to%20nine%20years%2C%20we%20were%20going%20with%20another%20vendor.%20Once%20we%20began%20using%20their%20composters%2C%20however%2C%20we%20realised%20that%20there%20was%20a%20lot%20of%20methane%20getting%20released.%20Around%20three%20years%20ago%2C%20we%20approached%20Waste%20Is%20Gold%20Technologies.%20Their%20machines%20are%20working%20well%20and%20we%E2%80%99ve%20had%20no%20complaints%20so%20far%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EExplaining%20further%20how%20beneficial%20this%20switch%20between%20machines%20has%20been%20for%20them%2C%20Setty%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CWhat%E2%80%99s%20different%20about%20the%20Waste%20Is%20Gold%20composters%20is%20that%20they%20generate%20compost%20on%20the%20same%20day%20the%20organic%20waste%20is%20processed.%20In%20the%20machines%20we%20used%20earlier%2C%20it%20would%20take%20three%20days%20to%20generate%20that%20compost.%20The%20compost%20we%E2%80%99re%20generating%20is%20being%20used%20for%20landscaping%20purposes%20on%20our%20properties.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%20%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw