ses-sports-to-help-rural-girls-study-in-school-sportz-village%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esports%20fraternity%3C%2Fa%3E.%20His%20zeal%20was%20among%20the%20many%20qualities%20that%20were%20saluted.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20story%20goes%20that%20in%20the%201970s%2C%20Sharma%20who%20frequently%20organised%20softball%20tournaments%20for%20school%20and%20college-going%20girls%2C%20was%20keeping%20a%20close%20eye%20on%20women%E2%80%99s%20cricket%20unfolding%20in%20England%20and%20Australia.%20Keen%20for%20Indian%20women%20to%20access%20these%20opportunities%2C%20he%20hatched%20a%20plan.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20morning%20the%20people%20of%20Lucknow%20woke%20up%20to%20clarion%20calls%20of%20%3Cem%3E%E2%80%9CKanyaon%20ki%20cricket%20hogi%2C%20zaroor%20aaiye%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fem%3E%20(Girls%20will%20be%20playing%20cricket%2C%20do%20come).%20The%20amplified%20voice%20belonged%20to%20none%20other%20than%20Sharma%2C%20who%20grouped%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F321379%2Fmaitrayana-uses-netball-sports-to-educate-and-empower-young-girls%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Einterested%20women%3C%2Fa%3E%20into%20the%20first%20association%20for%20women%E2%80%99s%20cricket%20in%20India.%20It%20was%20called%20the%20Women%E2%80%99s%20Cricket%20Association%20of%20India%20(WCAI)%20and%20was%20officially%20registered%20under%20the%20Societies%20Act%20of%20Lucknow%20in%201973.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnother%20all-rounder%20in%20cricket%2C%20Kapil%20Dev%20was%20known%20for%20his%20leadership%20both%20on%20and%20off-field.%20A%20milestone%20feat%20in%20Dev%E2%80%99s%20career%20was%20captaining%20the%20Indian%20team%20that%20won%20the%201983%20Cricket%20World%20Cup.%20On%20the%20eve%20of%20the%20match%2C%20as%20he%20spoke%20to%20the%20team%20encouragingly%20saying%2C%20%E2%80%9CWe%20can%20beat%20the%20mighty%20West%20Indies%2C%E2%80%9D%20they%20highly%20doubted%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20they%20were%20proved%20wrong%2C%20as%20hours%20later%2C%20Dev%20lifted%20the%20trophy%20becoming%20the%20first%20Indian%20skipper%20to%20do%20so.%20Recalling%20his%20pep%20talk%20in%20an%20interview%20with%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Times%20of%20India%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20he%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CAs%20a%20captain%2C%20you%20have%20to%20make%20sure%20that%20if%20you%20rub%20those%20kinds%20of%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F321082%2Fgoa-katya-ida-coelho-first-indian-female-windfoiler-iqfoiler-qualifies-for-asian-games%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epositive%20words%3C%2Fa%3E%20into%20the%20team%2C%20it%20will%20work.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E2.%20Sporting%20legends%20who%20proved%20their%20mettle%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201080px)%20100vw%2C%201080px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2FTimelapse-Frame-13-1695044067.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221080%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2FTimelapse-Frame-13-1695044067.jpg%201080w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2FTimelapse-Frame-13-1695044067-300x300.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2FTimelapse-Frame-13-1695044067-500x500.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2FTimelapse-Frame-13-1695044067-150x150.jpg%20150w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2FTimelapse-Frame-13-1695044067-768x768.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2FTimelapse-Frame-13-1695044067-96x96.jpg%2096w%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221080%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201080px)%20100vw%2C%201080px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2FTimelapse-Frame-14-1695044066.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221080%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2FTimelapse-Frame-14-1695044066.jpg%201080w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2FTimelapse-Frame-14-1695044066-300x300.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2FTimelapse-Frame-14-1695044066-500x500.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2FTimelapse-Frame-14-1695044066-150x150.jpg%20150w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2FTimelapse-Frame-14-1695044066-768x768.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2FTimelapse-Frame-14-1695044066-96x96.jpg%2096w%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221080%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cp%3EV%20P%20Sathyan%20started%20his%20career%20with%20the%20Kerala%20State%20Team%20and%20went%20on%20to%20great%20heights.%20His%20fans%20remember%20the%20footballer%E2%80%99s%20magnificent%2035-yard%20footer%20in%20the%201986%20Merdeka%20tournament%20against%20South%20Korea%2C%20which%20took%20India%20into%20the%20semi-finals.%20But%20many%20would%20argue%20that%20his%201992%20game%2C%20which%20helped%20end%20Kerala%E2%80%99s%2017-year%20Santosh%20Trophy%20title%20drought%2C%20was%20equally%20fascinating.%20Sathyan%20was%20also%20part%20of%20the%20India%20squad%20that%20cantered%20to%20a%20gold-medal%20finish%20at%20the%201995%20SAF%20Games%20in%20Chennai.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJo%20Paul%20Ancheri%20who%20played%20under%20Sathyan%E2%80%99s%20captaincy%20shared%20his%20dynamic.%20The%20former%20was%20widely%20regarded%20for%20his%20ability%20to%20play%20in%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F318867%2Ffirst-woman-indian-footballer-to-play-english-league-she-kicks-academy-underprivileged-girls-aditi-chauhan%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emultiple%20positions%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20defensive%20midfielder%2C%20midfielder%2C%20and%20striker.%20His%20stellar%20performances%20during%20the%201993%E2%80%931994%20season%20established%20him%20as%20one%20of%20the%20best%20players%20in%20the%20country.%20Shortly%20after%20the%20season%2C%20he%20got%20a%20call%20to%20play%20for%20the%20Indian%20National%20Team.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIM%20Vijayan%E2%80%99s%20rise%20from%20poverty%20to%20stardom%20is%20a%20story%20for%20the%20books.%20As%20a%20child%2C%20he%20sold%20eatables%20in%20the%20Thrissur%20Corporation%20stadium%2C%20ironically%2C%20the%20same%20place%20that%20shaped%20his%20passion%20for%20the%20game%20and%20his%20career%20thereafter.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EVijayan%E2%80%99s%20love%20for%20football%20was%20spotted%20by%20Mr%20M%20K%20Joseph%2C%20the%20former%20DGP%20of%20Kerala%2C%20who%20took%20to%20the%20boy%20and%20adopted%20him%20into%20the%20Kerala%20Police%20%E2%80%94%20where%20the%20former%20started%20his%20club%20career%20in%201989.%20The%20rest%20is%20history.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20list%20of%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F318215%2Fdelhi-boxer-rohit-tokas-won-bronze-medal-commonwealth-games-2022-despite-knee-injuries%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Egreat%20personalities%20%3C%2Fa%3Ein%20football%20would%20be%20incomplete%20without%20the%20name%20of%20S%20A%20Rahim.%20This%20%E2%80%98Architect%20of%20Modern%20Football%E2%80%99%20led%20the%20team%20to%20gold%20medals%20at%20the%201951%20and%201962%20Asian%20Games%2C%20along%20with%20moulding%20many%20players.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20teacher-turned-football%20coach%20is%20also%20credited%20with%20starting%20football%20groups%20across%20Andhra%20Pradesh%2C%20some%20of%20which%20are%20still%20functional%20today.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20these%20men%20made%20their%20mark%20on%20the%20field%2C%20Arjuna%20Award%20(1983)%20and%20Padma%20Shri%20(1985)%20awardee%20PT%20Usha%20made%20it%20on%20th