0the%20school%20into%20a%20mecca%20of%20learning%2C%20offering%20holistic%20growth%20through%20a%20variety%20of%20extra-curricular%20activities.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20seeds%20of%20change%20were%20sown%20in%20Archana%E2%80%99s%20mind%20at%20home.%20She%20saw%20her%20grandfather%2C%20a%20teacher%2C%20serve%20students.%20%E2%80%9CMy%20grandfather%20would%20teach%20a%20lot%20of%20tribal%20students.%20He%20used%20to%20teach%20them%20at%20our%20house%20and%20helped%20them%20in%20their%20higher%20studies.%20I%20aspired%20to%20be%20like%20him%20and%20help%20students%2C%E2%80%9D%20adds%20the%20teacher.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EWhere%20it%20all%20began%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20862px)%20100vw%2C%20862px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2FWhatsApp-Image-2023-09-10-at-11.25.39-1694697068.jpeg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22862%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Archana%20Nooguri%20with%20the%20students%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2FWhatsApp-Image-2023-09-10-at-11.25.39-1694697068.jpeg%20862w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2FWhatsApp-Image-2023-09-10-at-11.25.39-1694697068-300x214.jpeg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2FWhatsApp-Image-2023-09-10-at-11.25.39-1694697068-500x356.jpeg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2FWhatsApp-Image-2023-09-10-at-11.25.39-1694697068-768x547.jpeg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2FWhatsApp-Image-2023-09-10-at-11.25.39-1694697068-150x107.jpeg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-329945%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22614%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EArchana%20Nooguri%20with%20her%20students.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cp%3ERebbenapally%2C%