igcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EStarting%20with%20just%20100%20poultry%20hens%2C%20Ravindra%20now%20owns%201.8%20lakh%20hens%20on%20his%2050-acre%20farm%20in%20Amravati.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20getting%20a%2015-day%20training%20from%20the%20government%20department%2C%20he%20set%20up%20a%20poultry%20farm%20with%20100%20hens%20on%20a%20%3Cem%3Ekachha%20%3C%2Fem%3E(mud)%20slab%20in%20his%20house.%20Having%20no%20prior%20experience%2C%20he%20had%20to%20sell%20eggs%20and%20broilers%20at%20a%20low%20cost%20compared%20to%20the%20market.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGradually%2C%20Ravindra%20was%20able%20to%20expand%20his%20small%20business.%20He%20went%20from%20having%20100%20to%20400%20hens%20within%2010%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20this%20period%2C%20Ravindra%20completed%20his%20master%E2%80%99s%20in%20commerce%20in%201992%2C%20and%20four%20years%20later%2C%20got%20married.%20%E2%80%9CSince%20we%20came%20from%20an%20impoverished%20family%20and%20I%20was%20a%20farmer%2C%20many%20families%20rejected%20me%20for%20their%20daughters.%20Only%20after%20a%20lot%20of%20assurances%20from%20others%20was%20I%20able%20to%20get%20married%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20recalls.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20Ravindra%20bought%20an%20acre%20of%20land%20in%20Amravati.%20With%20a%20bank%20loan%20of%20Rs%205%20lakh%2C%20he%20expanded%20the%20farm%20with%204%2C000%20hens.%20%E2%80%9CBy%20then%2C%20I%20started%20earning%20well%20from%20the%20business%20and%20got%20my%20%3Cem%3Ekachaa%20%3C%2Fem%3Ehouse%20renovated.%20Soon%20after%2C%20I%20expanded%20the%20farm%20to%2012%2C000%20hens%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20his%20happiness%20was%20short-lived.%20In%202006%2C%20India%20witnessed%20an%20outbreak%20of%20bird%20flu%20that%20took%20a%20toll%20on%20the%20poultry%20business.%20%E2%80%9CIt%20was%20the%20first%20bird%20flu%20in%20the%20country.%20People%20were%20scared%20to%20consume%20broilers%20and%20eggs.%20They%20even%20forced%20poultry%20farmers%20to%20kill%20their%20birds.%20I%20sold%2016%2C000%20broilers%20for%20Rs%202%E2%80%933%20per%20kg%2C%20which%20were%20earlier%20sold%20at%20Rs%2050%E2%80%9360%20per%20kg%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2Famravati-3-1694610856.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Over%20the%20years%2C%20Ravindra%20advanced%20his%20farm%20with%20improved%20technologies.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2Famravati-3-1694610856.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2Famravati-3-1694610856-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2Famravati-3-1694610856-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2Famravati-3-1694610856-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2Famravati-3-1694610856-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-329823%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EOver%20the%20years%2C%20Ravindra%20advanced%20his%20farm%20with%20improved%20technologies.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CBut%20thankfully%2C%20I%20already%20had%20bought%2015-acre%20land%20to%20practise%20farming.%20So%20for%20those%20two%20years%2C%20I%20continued%20to%20earn%20by%20growing%20fruits%20and%20vegetables%20like%20oranges%2C%20soybean%2C%20and%20%3Cem%3Etuar%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Cem%3Edal%20%3C%2Fem%3E(pigeon%20pea)%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%202008%2C%20he%20took%20a%20loan%20of%20Rs%2025%20lakh%20from%20a%20bank%20and%20restarted%20the%20business%20with%2020%2C000%20egg-laying%20hens.%20%E2%80%9CWith%20profits%2C%20I%20kept%20on%20increasing%20the%20birds%20at%20my%20farm.%20Today%2C%20I%20have%201.8%20lakh%20hens%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Ravindra%2C%20who%20has%20been%20doing%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F54545%2Fwomen-farmers-empowerment-fighting-maharashtra-drought%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epoultry%20farming%20%3C%2Fa%3Efor%20the%20past%20four%20decades.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20shares%20that%20he%20now%20earns%20up%20to%20Rs%2060%2C000%20per%20day%20through%20this%20business.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ESharing%20learnings%20with%20new%20IAS%20officers%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EOver%20the%20years%2C%20Ravindra%20advanced%20his%20farm%20with%20improved%20technologies%20like%20indoor%20vertical%20farming%2C%20greenhouse%20farming%2C%20automatic%20watering%2C%20drip%20systems%2C%20remote%20sensing%20irrigation%20systems%2C%20and%20organic%20farming.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20have%20employed%20only%2050%20workers%20to%20manage%20my%20poultry%20farm%20spread%20across%2050%20acres.%20Most%20of%20the%20work%20is%20automated.%20For%20example%2C%20from%20collecting%20eggs%20from%20broilers%20and%20giving%20feed%20to%20poultry%20birds%2C%20to%20collecting%20their%20excreta%2C%20everything%20is%20ensured%20using%20machines%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20informs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EInterestingly%2C%20in%202013%2C%20he%20was%20selected%20by%20the%20state%20government%20as%20one%20of%20the%2080%20progressive%20farmers%20to%20be%20sent%20to%20Europe%20for%20a%2010-day%20trip%20to%20understand%20the%20nitty-gritty%20of%20expanding%20the%20farming%20business%20with%20machinery.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2Famravati-1694610755.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22In%202022%2C%20Ravindra%20was%20also%20conferred%20with%20the%20prestigious%